\id JOS  
\h Josuwa 
\toc1 Joshua 
\toc2 Josuwa 
\toc3 Jos 
\mt1 Josuwa  
\is1 Utu i viva  
\ip Buk ‚ÄúRaŇčgi‚ÄĚ i utuŇča Mosese va i vaŇčguŇčgiya Isirel na th…® raka raŇčgi Ijipt e t…®ne. Kaiwae Isirel mava th…® loŇčweghath…® na thovuya Loi, iya kaiwae ghanjilith…® vambema th…® rakaraka v…®v…® eŇčge e vuruvuru vwatavwata theghathegha ghwevar…® e t…®ne. Thako wolagh…®ye iyava th…® raka raŇčgiko Ijipt e t…®ne vama thiya marevao, na vama th…® mare varevaleŇčgi eŇčge Josuwa na Keleb.  
\ip Buk…®ke iyake i utuŇča Mosese le mare e ghereiye amba Josuwa i vaŇčguŇčgiya Isirel na veth…® raka raŇčgi Kenan na th…® wo vanautumako iyako.  
\c 1  
\s1 Loi i utu vavur…®gheghe weya Josuwa  
\p
\v 1 Mosese, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo, vama i mare na e ghereiye, amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe Josuwa, Nan nariye na Mosese va gharathalavu, iŇča,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúLo rakakaiwo Mosese kaero i mare. E mbaŇčake iyake u vivatha weiniyaŇčgi Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyena wolagh…®ye, hu raka lawa Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan, na hu raka e thivathiva regha, mbaŇča nasiye amba ne ya wogiya weŇčga.  
\v 3 The val…®vaŇčga ne vohu vur…®ghath…® e gheghemina kaero ya vatomwe e ghemi, Ňčgoreiye va ya dagerawe Mosese.  
\v 4 Val…®vaŇčgana wolagh…®ye ne ya wogiya weŇčga, iri e vuruvuru vwatavwata e yaghalako, i ruwoko e ghaiwabuniyeko ve wo Lebenon ououniye. Lemi val…®vaŇčga ne ve wo Walagh…®ta Iupreitis e boimako. I wo Hiti lenji val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye na i njaoko e yalasiniyeko ve njogha Njigh…® Meditareiniyan ghadidiye.  
\v 5 Ma lolo regha ne i kivwalaŇčge mbaŇča ambane e yawayawalin. Ne ya thalavuŇčge Ňčgora va ya thalavu Mosese, mane ya roiteteŇčge, mbene weiŇčgu vara ghen mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye.  
\v 6 U vur…®gheghe na u gharematuwo, kaiwae ghen iya ne u vaŇčguŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake na vohu yaku e thivathivako iya va ya dagera weŇčgi orumburumbumi.   
\p
\v 7 ‚ÄúMbema u vur…®gheghe eŇčge na gharen…®na i matuwo. U njimbukikiŇčge na mbarona iya lo rakakaiwo Mosese va i wogiyana e ghen, u ghambu. Thava u goriwoyathu mbaro nasiye regha, mbala the bigithan u vakatha ne val…®kaiwan moli.  
\v 8 U renuwaŇčakiki na u vaona valaŇča Mbaro gha Buk. Gougou na ghararagh…®ye u rerenuwaŇča kaiwae, mbala u vakatha wagiyawe bigibigike wolagh…®ye va th…® rorinjoŇčaŇčgi e t…®ne. Mbala budakai u vakatha ne val…®kaiwan moli.  
\v 9 Kaero ma utuŇča e ghen. Mbema u vur…®gheghe eŇčge na gharen…®na i matuwo. Thava u mararu na u gharelagh…®lagh…®, kaiwae the val…®vaŇčga ne u reŇčawe, ghino \nd Giya Loi\nd* len Loi mbene weiŇčgu vara ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\s1 Josuwa i utu weŇčgiya uu Rubin, Gad na Manase  
\p
\v 10 Josuwa i dage weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko lenji randevivaŇčgi, iŇča,  
\v 11 ‚ÄúHu raka weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko e lenji kiyamu, na vohu giya yanawanji huŇča, ‚ÄėHu vivathaŇča lemi bigibigi na ghami, kaiwae ma mbaŇča mbaŇčato eŇčge inawe, amba ra rakalawa Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan na vara wo thivathivako iya \nd Giya Loi\nd* la Loi ne i wogiya weinda na ghambanda.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 12 Josuwa mbowo i dage weŇčgiva uu Rubin, uu Gad na uu Manase vaŇčgothiye, iŇča,  
\v 13 ‚ÄúHu renuwaŇčakiki \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo Mosese va le utuutu e ghemi, iŇča, ‚Äė\nd Giya Loi\nd* lemi Loi kaero i wogiya thelauke iyake e ghemi na val…®vaŇčgake iyake ghambami.‚Äô  
\v 14 Wo hu iteteŇčgi lemi ovo, lemi ŇčgaŇčga na lemi thetheghan burumwaka, sip na gout gheke. Wo th…® reyaku e thivathivake iya Mosese va i wogiyake e ghemi, Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro. Ko iyemaeŇčge lemi ragagaith…®na wolagh…®ye weinji lenji gaith…®na bigibiginiye wolagh…®ye e n…®manji, th…® raka viva lenji val…® Isirel e ghamwanji na veth…® raka lawa Jor…®dan. Wo hu thalavuime, oghaghamike ghime,  
\v 15 ghaghad…® \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i wogiya thivathiva weŇčgi na veth…® towowe, Ňčgora va i vakatha e ghemi. Na ghaghad…® thiye tembene veth…® wova lenji thelau, \nd Giya Loi\nd* lemi Loi ne i wogiya weŇčgi. Iyako e ghereiye amba hu rakanjogha na vohu yakuŇča lemi thelau, iyava \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo Mosese i wogiya weŇčga, Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako Ňčgora varaeko le ghamba yovoro.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Amba th…® gonjoghawe Josuwa, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBudakai u utugiya weime ne wo vakatha Ňčgoreiye. Na the val…®vaŇčga u variyeimewe ne wo rakawe.  
\v 17 Ňägora va wo ghambu Mosese ghal…®Ňčae, tembene wo ghambuŇčgeva, thoŇčgo \nd Giya Loi\nd* len Loi weiye ghen Ňčgora va weiye Mosese.  
\v 18 Thela thoŇčgo i wovanjovanjoŇčge na ma i ghambu ghal…®Ňčan ne wo tagavamare. Mbema u vur…®gheghe eŇčge na gharen…®na i matuwo.‚ÄĚ   
\c 2  
\s1 Reihab na rakelakela theghewo  
\p
\v 1 Ghemba Sitim e t…®ne, Josuwa, Nan nariye, i variye thuwoleŇčgiya rakelakela theghewo, iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa na vohu ghaelawa Walagh…®tae Jor…®dan na vohu kelaŇča Kenan thivathivaniye, iyavara ghembana Jeriko.‚ÄĚ Amba ghar…®ghar…®ma theghewo veth…® ghaelawa Jor…®dan na veth…® ru Jeriko. Th…® ru wevo rayathiyathima eunda, idae Reihab ele Ňčgolo na th…® ghenawe gougouko iyako.  
\v 2 Ghar…®ghar…® vavana th…® giya Jeriko lenji kiŇč yanawae, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMe gougou Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye vavana th…® mena th…® kela e ghembake t…®ne.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Kaero kiŇč…®ko i variyeŇčgiya le ravarivariye weya Reihab, iŇča, ‚ÄúU vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®na menda th…® ru e len Ňčgolona t…®ne, kaiwae th…® mena th…® kelaŇča ghembake lagh…®ye t…®ne.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4-6 Amba muyai kiŇč…®ko le ravarivariye veth…® vutha weya Reihab, mbe kaero me vaŇčguvoreŇčaŇčgiya rakelakelama e Ňčgoloko gha bwana yavoro moli na i vaŇčguthuwoleŇčgi e nana p…®laks wak…®wak…®ye raberabe. IwaeŇčge Reihab i dage weŇčgiya ravarivariyeko, iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru, ghar…®ghar…®na menda th…® mena elo Ňčgoloke, ko iyemaeŇčge ma ya ghareghare aŇčga menda th…® mena. Menda Ňčgora thela i ghaona kaero veth…® raŇčgi; ghamba ruko ghambaŇča vara th…® kigh…®. Ma ya ghareghare aŇčga menda th…® reŇča. Ma hu vamayaŇča eŇčge hu reghamba weŇčgi. Mbwata ne val…®kaiwami hu la vuthavaidiŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Kaero kiŇč…®ko le ravarivariye veth…® raka raŇčgi na e ghereinji amba th…® ki ghamba ruko. Th…® raka reghamba weŇčgiya rakelakelama na veth…® ghad vara e ghamba ghaeghaelawa Jor…®dan.   
\p
\v 8 Amba muyai rakelakelama th…® ghena, Reihab i wa ve voro weŇčgi e Ňčgoloko vwatae,  
\v 9 na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa ghareghare Loi kaero i giya val…®vaŇčgake iyake weŇčga, na ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ghime e ghembake iyake t…®ne wo mararu lagh…®ye moli kaiwami.  
\v 10 Wo loŇčwa utunimi mbaŇča va hu raka raŇčgi Ijipt e t…®ne na Giya i tagaviya Njigh…® Sosoro na i meme e ghamwami na hu raka lawawe. Na tembe wo loŇčweva Amori lenji kiŇč theghewo Saihon na Og, weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ghar…®ghar…® hu mukuwoŇčgi Jor…®dan e boimaniyeko.  
\v 11 MbaŇča wo loŇčwa utunimi woya mararu lagh…®ye moli na lama vur…®ghegheke wolagh…®ye iko, kaiwae wo ghareghare Giya lemi Loi iye buruburu yavoroke na yambane ghanji Loi.  
\v 12 E mbaŇčake vara iyake hu tholo Giya e idae, na mbaŇča ne hu wo Jeriko, ne hu mwaewo weŇčgiya lo bodabodake Ňčgoreiya ghino ya mwaewo weŇčga.  
\v 13 Wo hu utugiyama nono regha na ya ghareghare emunjoru weiŇčguyaŇčgiya bwebwe na nava, olouŇčguko na oghaghaŇčguko, weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ŇčgaŇčga mane hu mukuwoime, ko iyemaeŇčge ne hu vamoruime mare e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Rakelakelako th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúYawalimina ne modaya yawal…®meke, thoŇčgo mane wo vamboromboro lama dagera weŇčge. ThoŇčgo mane u giya lolo regha yanawae budakaiya wo vakavakathake, mbaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i wogiya val…®vaŇčgake iyake weime ne wo mwaewo weŇčga na wo vamoruŇčga.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 Amba i vakuki njoŇčaŇčgiya ghewoko e thiyo, e dedele regha, kaiwae Ňčgoloko va th…® vatad…® vatabo weiye ghembako gha gana.  
\v 16 Elako i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wao e ououko r…®ghenji, na thava kiŇč…®ko le ratamwetamwe th…® vaidiŇčga. Mbowo vohu kubaro gheko mbaŇča thegheto, ghaghad ghamiratamwetamweko th…® raka njogha amba vohu raka reŇča e lemi kamwath…®ko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Kaero gh…®mogh…®moruko th…® dage weya Reihab th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhime weime, dagerake iya moŇča na wo vakathake e ghen mane Ňčgar…®ime, mbene ghen vara u vakowana mbaroke iyake.  
\v 18 MbaŇča ne wo ru e lemi val…®vaŇčgake, u Ňčgara thiyona sosoro iya mwo liveŇčgena e dedeleke iya mo vakukinjoŇčaimewe, na u vaŇčguruwoŇčgiya rama na t…®na, olou na len bodabodana wolagh…®ye e len Ňčgolona t…®ne.  
\v 19 Thela thoŇčgo i raŇčgi e len Ňčgolona t…®ne na i mare, tembe ghamberegha i vaidiya le thar…®ko modae, ghawonjowe mane i mena weime. Ko thoŇčgo regha e len Ňčgolona t…®ne i vaidiya vuyowo, modae ghime ne wo vaidi.  
\v 20 ThoŇčgo u utuutu menda wo mena budakai kaiwae, mane wo vamboromboro lama dagera e ghen.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 Reihab iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero Ňčgoreiye mohuŇčana.‚ÄĚ I variye yathuŇčgi na elagh…®niye i liya thiyoma sosoro na i Ňčgar…® e dedeleko.   
\p
\v 22 MbaŇča th…® wareri, th…® wa e ououko r…®ghenji na veth…® yakuwe mbaŇča mbaŇčato. Ratamwetamwema th…® tamwe takwa val…®vaŇčgako wolagh…®ye na th…® raka njogha ma th…® ndevaidiŇčgi mun.  
\v 23 Amba rakelakelama theghewo th…® njama e bobokuluko, th…® lawa Jor…®dan na th…® njogha weya Josuwa. Th…® utugiyawe bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va th…® yomarako weŇčgi.  
\v 24 Th…® dage weya Josuwa th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru Giya kaero i wogiya weinda ghembako lagh…®ye. Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® mararu lagh…®ye kaiwanda.‚ÄĚ   
\c 3  
\p  
\s1 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® raka lawa Jor…®dan  
\p
\v 1 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča, Josuwa na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye th…® raka iteta Sitim na th…® raka e walagh…®ta Jor…®dan ghadidiye. Mbowo thiya yaku eŇčge gheko, th…® roroghagha lenji rakalawa kaiwae.  
\v 2 MbaŇča mbaŇčato e ghereiye randevivako th…® vagh…®liya kiyamuko lagh…®ye,  
\v 3 na th…® dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne hu thuwe ravowovowo th…® th…®na Giya la Loi le Dagerawe gha Bogis, amba hu raka itete lemi kiyamuna, na hu raka reghamba weŇčgi.  
\v 4 Thiye ne th…® viva weŇčga kaiwae ma mbaŇča regha va hu rakaraka mena e val…®vaŇčgake iyake. Ne hu ndevur…®thai Dagerake gha Bogis ghadidiye. Mbe e ghami lughawoghawo Ňčgoreiye kilo mita regha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Josuwa i dage weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vaboboma ghamimberegha, kaiwae evole Giya ne i vakathaŇčgi vakatha amba rotaele vavana e t…®nendake.‚ÄĚ  
\v 6 Amba Josuwa i dage weŇčgi ravowovowoko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wora Dagerana gha Bogis e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®lemi na hu viva ghar…®ghar…®na e ghamwanji.‚ÄĚ Kaero th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye Josuwa le utu weŇčgi.   
\p
\v 7 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúNoroke ya wora idan gha wovorovoroŇča r…®ghe wabwi Isirel e maranji. Na mbala th…® ghareghare ghino weiŇčgu ghen Ňčgora va weiŇčgu Mosese.  
\v 8 U dage weŇčgi ravowovowona iya th…® th…®na Dagerana gha Bogis, uŇča, ‚ÄėMbaŇča ne hu vutha e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan ghadidiye, hu ghaenja na vohu ndethin e mbwako t…®ne.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Kaero Josuwa i dage weŇčgi Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye, iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu raka mena gheke na ya utuŇča Giya la Loi ghal…®Ňčae na ra loŇčwe.  
\v 10 Ne e kamwath…®ke iyake amba hu ghareghare Loi e yawayawaliye ina weinda, na emunjoru amalagh…®niye ne i vagegeyathuŇčgiya Kenan, Hiti, Hivi, Perisi, Gegasi, Amori na Jebusi ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwami.  
\v 11 Wo hu thuwe, yambaneke lagh…®ye gha Giya le Dagerawe gha Bogis ne veth…® wonjakai e ghamwami e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan.  
\v 12 MbaŇčake hu tuthiŇčgi gh…®mogh…®moru theyaworo na theghewo Isirel e gha uu regha na regha t…®nenji.  
\v 13 Na mbaŇčaniye vara ravowovowoko ne th…® kewe \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dagerako gha Bogis na veth…® ghaenja e mbwako t…®ne, ne i voru towo na i voru vavatha na regha.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 MbaŇča Isirel vama th…® raka itete kiyamuko na math…® raka ghembeya Jor…®dan, amba ravowovowoko th…® kewa viva Dagerako gha Bogis, e ghamwanji.  
\v 15 Kaiwae uloulo va gha mbaŇča, uye tembe gha mbaŇčava e val…®vaŇčgako iyako, iya kaiwae ŇčgonuŇčgo va i voru e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča ravowovowoko va th…® kewa Bogis…®ko th…® vur…®thai mbwako ghadidiye na th…® vur…®utu e mbwako t…®ne,  
\v 16 mbaŇčara mbwako i voru ndeghath…® Ňčgora va i voru njamakowe. Va i voru vavatha mbe bwagabwaga weŇčgi e ghemba regha idae Adam, Jeretan ele val…®vaŇčga, ko mbwako val…®vaŇčga i raŇčgiraŇčgi na ve wo Njigh…® Maremareniye va i ma moli. Iyako va i vakatha ghar…®ghar…®ko val…®kaiwanji th…® raka lawa Jeriko ghadidiye.  
\v 17 MbaŇča Isirel va th…® rakarakalawa, ravowovowoko iyava th…® kewa Giya le Dagerako gha Bogis mbe th…® ndekikiyaŇča vara e thelau momoe Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan e t…®ne, ghaghad ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® rakalawavao.   
\c 4  
\p  
\s1 Josuwa i vathe var…®var…® Isirel ghanjirenuwaŇčakiki  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Isirel vama th…® rakalawavao, amba Giya i dagewe Josuwa, iŇča,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúU tuthiŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru theyaworo na theghewo, regha iya i mena e uu regha t…®ne.  
\v 3 Na u dage weŇčgi th…® mbana var…®var…® var…®yaworo na var…®iwo e walagh…®tana yamoe moli, Ňčgora vara ravowovowona th…® ndeghath…®nawe. Th…® mban na veth…® bigirawe Ňčgora vara ne vohu ghenanawe gougouke noroke.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 Amba Josuwa i kula vathaŇčgi gh…®mogh…®moruma theyaworo na theghewoma Isirel e t…®nenjima, regha iya uu regha e t…®ne,  
\v 5 na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu raka na vohu rakanja Jor…®dan. Hu viva \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dagerana gha Bogis e ghamwae. Regha iya i wo var…® regha na i wora e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le, na var…® regha iya i ndeth…® Isirel gha uu.  
\v 6 Var…®var…®ke thiyake nevole th…® vanuwov…®r…®inda budakai Giya va i vakatha weinda. ThoŇčgovole mbaŇča i menamenako na lemi ŇčgaŇčga th…® vaitoŇčga na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėVar…®var…®ke thiyake ŇčgoroŇčga ghanjirumwaru?‚Äô  
\v 7 Kaero huŇča, ‚ÄėVa e mbaŇčako iyako walagh…®ta Jor…®dan i meme mbaŇča th…® th…®n…®lawa \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dagera gha Bogis gheke.‚Äô Var…®var…®ke thiyake ne i vavanuwov…®r…®Ňčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Isirel tha na tha budakai va i yomara gheke.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Gh…®mogh…®moruko th…® vamboromboro Josuwa le renuwaŇčako Ňčgoreiya Giya va i dage weya Josuwa. Va th…® mbana var…®var…® var…®yaworo na var…®iwo e walagh…®ta Jor…®dan yamoe moli, Ňčgora uu Isirel lenji ghanaghanagha. Th…® mban na veth…® bigira Ňčgora vara lenji kiyamuko inawe.  
\v 9 Josuwa vambe i bigirava var…®var…® var…®yaworo na var…®iwo e walagh…®tako yamoe, Ňčgora vara ravowovowo va th…® ndeghath…®we na th…® ndeth…®na Dageraweko gha Bogis. (Var…®var…®ke thiyake mbe inanjiwe e mbaŇčake iyake.)   
\p
\v 10 Ravowovowoko vambe th…® ndethin vara bogis…®ko e walagh…®tako yamoe moli ghaghad…® th…® vakathavao bigibigiko wolagh…®ye \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i dage weya Josuwa na i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® vakatha. Utuutuke wolagh…®ye thiyake Mosese va i utugiya weya Josuwa. Ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® vamayaŇča th…® raka lawa e walagh…®tako.  
\v 11 MbaŇča ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye vama inanji val…®mbwa, na e maranji amba ravowovowoko th…® th…®na Dagerako gha Bogis na th…® viva ghar…®ghar…®ko e ghamwanji.  
\v 12 Gh…®mogh…®moru va inanji Rubin na Gad e ghanji uu t…®nenji na Manase gha uu vaŇčgothiye t…®ne, th…® vivatha gaith…® kaiwae na th…® viva ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghamwanji, Ňčgora Mosese va le utuutu weŇčgi.  
\v 13 Va lenji ghanaghanagha poti tausan (40,000) iyava th…® raka lawa weinji \nd Giya Loi\nd* na veth…® raka vutha Jeriko malamoniye gaith…® kaiwae.   
\p
\v 14 E mbaŇčako iyako \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vamidi Josuwa Isirel taulagh…®ko e maranji, na th…® yavwatatawana yawaliyeko gha mbaŇča wolagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya va th…® yavwatatawana Mosese.   
\p
\v 15 Amba Loi i dage weya Josuwa iŇča,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúU dage weŇčgiya ravowovowona iya th…® th…®na Dagerana gha Bogis, th…® raka iteta Jor…®dan na th…® voroma e malavwatake.‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 Josuwa i vakatha Ňčgoreiye,  
\v 18 na mbaŇča ravowovowoko kaero inanji e malavwatako, amba mbwako i thothova, i voru na tembe ve vanat…®va vaŇčga na vaŇčga.   
\p
\v 19 Theghathegha gha manjala i viva moli gha mbaŇča mbaŇčayaworo e t…®ne, ghar…®ghar…®ko kaero th…® raka lawa Jor…®dan na vethiya kiyamu e ghemba regha idae Gilgal ghadidiye, ina Jeriko e boimaniyeko.  
\v 20 Var…®var…®ma var…®yaworo na var…®iwo me th…® mban…®ma e walagh…®ta Jor…®dan t…®ne, Josuwa i wabwi vatha e ghembako iyako.  
\v 21 Kaero Josuwa i dage weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko iŇča, ‚ÄúLemi ŇčgaŇčga mbaŇča muyaiko nevole th…® vaitoŇčga na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėVar…®var…®ke thiyake ŇčgoroŇčga ghanjirumwaru?‚Äô  
\v 22 hu dage weŇčgi huŇča, ‚ÄėVar…®var…®ke thiyake th…® vanuwov…®r…®inda va e mbaŇčako iyako walagh…®ta Jor…®dan i meme na ghime wo raka lawa e thelau momoe.‚Äô  
\v 23 Ne hu utu Ňčgora iyake, kaiwae Giya la Loi va i vakatha walagh…®ta Jor…®dan i meme kaiwame na wo raka lawa, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva va i vakatha Njigh…® Sosoro i meme na wo raka lawawe.  
\v 24 Va i vakatha Ňčgora iyako mbala ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke th…® ghareghare Giya iye Ravur…®gheghe, na ghemi hu yavwatatawana Giya la Loi mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Amori lenji kiŇč…®Ňčgi, Jor…®dan e yalasiniyeko na Kenan lenji kiŇč…®Ňčgi e Njigh…® Meditareiniyan ghadidiye, th…® loŇčwe toto, \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i vakatha Jor…®dan i meme ghaghad Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye va th…® raka lawavao val…®mbwa, i vakathaŇčgi th…® mararu na th…® gharelagh…®lagh…® lagh…®ye moli, ma tembe val…®kaiwanjiva th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgi.   
\s1 Gh…®mogh…®moru ghanjiten…®to Gilgal e t…®ne  
\p
\v 2 Giya i dagewe Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúHu piriya niboka na hu tena Isirel gh…®mogh…®moruna riwanji mbothiye njimwae.‚ÄĚ (Iyako va lenji vakatha mbaŇčaiwoniye.)  
\v 3 Kaero Josuwa i vakatha Ňčgoreiye \nd Giya Loi\nd* me dagewe na th…® ten…®Ňčgi Isirel gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye riwanji mbothiye njimwa. Na th…® rena ghembako iyako idae Njimwa Ghambaten.  
\v 4-6 MbaŇča Isirel va th…® raka itete Ijipt, gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye vama th…® wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye. Ko iyemaeŇčge, va lenji loŇčga e njam…®njam…®bwaga na gamagainiye mava th…® wo mun kiten…®yathu thanavuniye. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, gh…®mogh…®moruko iyava th…® raka raŇčgiko Ijipt, na ghanji theghatheghako vama val…®kaiwae gaith…®, va thiya marevao, kaiwae mava th…® ghambugha \nd Giya Loi\nd* le mbaro. Loi va i lith…® weŇčgi Ňčgora va le tholoko, thiye mane veth…® vaidi thivathivako iya bigithaŇčar…®ke veimaima na ndendewo, iya Loi va i dagerako weŇčgi orumburumbunji.  
\v 7 Josuwa va i la vakatha kiten…®yathu thanavuniye weŇčgi thako togha Gilgal e t…®ne, kaiwae oramanji mava th…® loŇčweghath…® \nd Giya Loi\nd* na th…® vakatha kiten…®yathu thanavuniye weŇčgi mbaŇča va e lenji loŇčga t…®ne.   
\p
\v 8 MbaŇča gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye vama th…® wo kiten…®yathu, taulagh…®ko mbowo thiya yaku e lenji kiyamuko ghaghad ghanji ten…®toko i moi.   
\p
\v 9 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe Josuwa, iŇča, ‚ÄúNoroke kaero ya tagayathu lemi mebwabwari na rakakaiwobwaga monjinaniye Ijipt va th…® vakatha weŇčga.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae, th…® rena ghembako idae Gilgal. Idako iyako mbe inawe noroke.   
\s1 Thaga ValaŇčani ghathaga  
\p
\v 10 MbaŇča Isirel vamba inanji Gilgal, Jeriko malamoniye e t…®ne, kaero th…® vakatha Thaga ValaŇčani gha renuwaŇčakiki, manjala gha mbaŇča mbaŇčayaworo na mbaŇčavar…® yegh…®yegh…®yeniye.  
\v 11 Thaga ValaŇčani vakathaniye e ghereiye na mbaŇčambaŇčava, kaero th…® raka veth…® vugha bali uneune e umauma t…®nenji Kenan t…®ne. Th…® kaghaege vavana, vavana th…® voŇčgoŇčgo na th…® vakatha bred ma weiye is…®t. Va e mbaŇčako iyako th…® ghan…®kai vara Kenan ghan…®Ňčganiye.  
\v 12 MbaŇčaniye vara th…® ghana Kenan ghan…®Ňčganiye, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vatowaŇča mana iri e buruburu. Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye ma tembe th…® ndevaidiva mun. E mbaŇčako iyako na iwa e ghamwanjiko th…® ghana ghan…®Ňčga th…® kabu Kenan e thivathivaniye.   
\b  
\s1 Va ŇčgoroŇčga na th…® wo Jeriko  
\p
\v 13 MbaŇča regha Josuwa va ina Jeriko ghadidiye na mbaŇča i tagath…®na marae kaero i thuwe gh…®moru regha i ndendeghath…® e ghamwae. Le gaith…® gha ghal…®th…® vama i mwanagita e ghambae na i ndewo e n…®mae. Josuwa i ndetha e ghad…®d…®ye na i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen ghama rathalavu regha e gaith…®ke o ghama th…®gh…®ya?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Amalako iŇča, ‚ÄúNandere, ghino ma ragagaith…® regha o ghami th…®gh…®ya, ko iyemaeŇčge ghino \nd Giya Loi\nd* le ragagaith…® lenji randeviva. Iya kaiwae ma menake.‚ÄĚ  
\p Josuwa weiye le yavwatata i wovakururuwo ghamwae i nja e thelauko vwatae na i kururuwe, iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, ghino len rakakaiwo. Nuwaniya ya vakatha budakai?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 Kaero \nd Giya Loi\nd* le ragagaith…®ma lenji randeviva i dagewe Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúU bigi raŇčgiya gheghen…®na ghae, kaiwae thelauna iya u ndendeghath…®nawe i boboma.‚ÄĚ Josuwa i vakatha Ňčgoreiya va i dagekowe.   
\c 6  
\p
\v 1 Jeriko iye ghemba lagh…®ye na va th…® gana vagh…®liya. Gha th…®n…®mbaŇčgiko wolagh…®ye va th…® ki vaoŇčgi na mbe e ghanji ragat…®gat…® na thava Isirel th…® raka ru. Na tembe th…® dage ten…®va thava tembe lolo regha i ruva o i raŇčgi e ghembako t…®ne.   
\p
\v 2 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, kaero ya worawa Jeriko e n…®man…®na ghare, weiye gha kiŇč…®ko na ragagaith…® vur…®vur…®ghegheniyeko wolagh…®ye.  
\v 3 MbaŇča regha na regha, ghen na len ragagaith…®na wolagh…®ye ne hu loŇčga vagh…®liya Jeriko, mbaŇčara iya mbaŇča theghewona e t…®nenji.  
\v 4 MbaŇča ghepir…®niye e t…®ne, ravowovowo theghepir…® ne th…® mbana ghanji mema vwarapir…®, iya sip…®na ghanji sokisoki, na th…® ndeviva Dagerawena e gha Bogis ghamwae. Ghemi na ravowovowona ne hu loŇčga vagh…®liya ghemba mbaŇčapir…® na thiye th…® uwiuwiya memaŇčgina.  
\v 5 MbaŇča ne hu loŇčwe th…® uwiya memako molao, taulagh…®na ghemi hu yaro na ghal…®Ňčami lagh…®ye. Ne mbaŇčara ganana i mav…®r…® na ragagaith…®na wolagh…®ye th…® raka ru Ňčgora regha na regha inanjiwe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 Kaero Josuwa, Nan nariye i kula vathaŇčgiya ravowovowoko na i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúHu th…®na \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dagerako gha Bogis, na hu th…®n…®ra e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®lemi na ghamunena theghepir…® th…® bigiya mema, th…® viva Bogis…®na e ghamwae na th…® viva e ghemi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Josuwa i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iŇča, ‚ÄúRa raka na vara ndevagh…®liya Jeriko. Ragagaith…®na vavana th…® raka viva Bogis…®ko e ghamwae.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 MbaŇča Josuwa i utuvao weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko kaero ravowovowoko theghepir…® th…® viva \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dagerako gha Bogis ghamwae na th…® uwiuwiya lenji memako.  
\v 9 Ragagaith…® vavana th…® raka viva memako gha rauwiuwi e ghamwanji na vavana th…® raka reghamba Bogis…®ko e ghereiye. E mbaŇčako iyako mema lenji randa eŇčge.  
\v 10 Ko iyemaeŇčge Josuwa i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko, iŇča, ‚ÄúNe hu ndeyaro, tha ghal…®Ňčami lagh…®ye, na ne hu ndegugwa utu regha, ghaghad ne the mbaŇča ya dage e ghemi yaŇča, hu yaro, ko amba hu yaro na ghal…®Ňčami lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 E mbaŇčako iyako rakewakewama kaero th…® kewa vagh…®liya ghembako, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dagerawe gha Bogis e mbaŇčako iyako Ňčgoreiya Josuwa me le utuutu weŇčgi, amba th…® raka njogha e lenji kiyamuko na veth…® ghenawe gougouko iyako.   
\p
\v 12 Igh…®viya, mbe mbaŇčambaŇča Josuwa i thuweiru, kaero ravowovowoko th…® kewava \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dageraweko gha Bogis.  
\v 13 Ravowovowoko theghepir…® iya th…® uwiuwiya memako th…® viva Bogis…®ko e ghamwae na ragagaith…® vavana th…® loŇčga viva rauwiuwi memako e ghamwanji na vavana Bogis…®ko e ghereiye. E mbaŇčako iyako mema mbe lenji randa eŇčge.  
\v 14 MbaŇča theghewoniyeko e t…®ne tembe th…® vagh…®liyava ghembako mbaŇčara na mbowo th…® njoghava e kiyamuko. MbaŇča theghewona e t…®nenji va th…® vakavakatha Ňčgora iyako.   
\p
\v 15 MbaŇča mbaŇčapir…®niye e t…®ne, igh…®viya rakaraka, Isirel th…® raka thuweiru na veth…® raka vagh…®liya Jeriko mbaŇčapir…®. Lenji vagh…®liyako iyako Ňčgoreiya va th…® vakavakatha mbaŇčawonama e t…®ne, ko va e mbaŇčako iyako t…®ne mbaŇčapir…® vara va th…® vagh…®liya ghembako.  
\v 16 Vagh…®liya mbaŇčapir…®ninji e t…®ne, ravowovowo th…® uwiya lenji memako ‚ÄĒ th…® uwi na molao, amba Josuwa i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iŇča, ‚ÄúHu yaro, kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero i wogiya ghembake iyake e ghemi.  
\v 17 Ghembake na bigibigike wolagh…®ye e t…®neke, ghar…®ghar…®niye, lenji thetheghan na lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye ra mukuwoŇčgi, kaiwae Loi le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye. Ko iyemaeŇčge Reihab ‚ÄĒ wevo rayathiyathima na le Ňčgolona gha rayakuyaku wolagh…®ye ne hu ndevakowanaŇčgi, kaiwae va i vaŇčgu thuweleŇčgiya la rakelakelama.  
\v 18 Budakai Loi va iŇča ne ra mukuwo, tene hu ndewova regha, ne iwaeŇčge tembe ghamimberegha hu vakatha ghami vuyowo, ko amba vuyowoko iyako i lawa ela kiyamuko na i mukuwoinda.  
\v 19 Bigibigiko wolagh…®ye th…® vakatha e silva, gol, kopa na aiyan ra bigi vakatha na ra vabobomaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaiwae na ra bigira bigibigi e ghambanji Loi ele Ňčgoloko t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 MbaŇča ravowovowoko th…® uwighath…®gha memaŇčgiko na ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® loŇčwe amba th…® yaro na ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye. E mbaŇčako vara iyako Jeriko gha gana i mav…®r…®. Ragagaith…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® raka ru Ňčgora vara va inanjikowe na th…® wo ghembako.  
\v 21 Va mbema th…® mukuwo vara ghembako. E lenji gaith…®ko gha ghalith…® th…® gaboŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru, wanakau, gamagai, amalagh…®sar…®, yalagh…®sar…®, lenji burumwaka, sip na doŇč…®ki, th…® mukuwoŇčgi moli.   
\p
\v 22 Amba Josuwa i dage weŇčgiya rakelakelama theghewoma iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa Reihab ele Ňčgolokona t…®ne na vohu vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgi gha mband…®mband…® na ghar…®ghar…®na wolagh…®ye ele Ňčgolona t…®ne Ňčgora va lemi dageranawe.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 Amba thetheghama iyava veth…® kelaŇča Jerikoma th…® wa na veth…® vaŇčguŇčgiya Reihab weiyaŇčgiya ramae na t…®nae, olouye na gha uuko ghar…®ghar…®niye wolagh…®ye na veth…® vaŇčguraweŇčgi Isirel e lenji kiyamuko ghadidiye eto.   
\p
\v 24 Amba th…® woŇčambu ghembako lagh…®ye weiye bigibiginiyeko wolagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge bigibigi va th…® vakathaŇčgi e gol, silva, kopa, brons na aiyan, th…® bigi na veth…® bigiraweŇčgi e ghambanji \nd Giya Loi\nd* ele Ňčgolo t…®ne.  
\v 25 Ko iyemaeŇčge Josuwa i vamora Reihab na le bodabodako wolagh…®ye, kaiwae va i vaŇčgu thuweleŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruma iyava veth…® kelama Jeriko. Reihab orumburumbuye mbe inanji wabwi Isirel e t…®nenji noroke.   
\p
\v 26 E mbaŇčako iyako Josuwa i tholo na iŇča, ‚ÄúThela nevole i mando na i vatad…® vaira Jeriko, \nd Giya Loi\nd* nevole i gura.  
\q1 Thela thoŇčgo i mando na i wora ganako r…®ghe gha mbagh…®mbagh…®, nariye gamau nevole i mare.  
\q1 Thela thoŇčgo i vatada ghamba ruruko, nariye vir…® reghamba nevole i mare.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 27 \nd Giya Loi\nd* vambe weiye vara Josuwa, i vakatha utuniye i lalu Kenani lagh…®yeko e t…®ne.   
\c 7  
\s1 Eikan le thar…®  
\p
\v 1 \nd Giya Loi\nd* le mbaro Isirel kaiwanji mbaŇča va th…® mena th…® mukuwo Jeriko mava th…® ghambu. E t…®nenjiko amala regha idae Eikan iyava i kivwala mbaroko iyako, iwaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* le ghatemuru lagh…®ye i yomara weŇčgiya Isirel. Eikan iye Kami nariye na Jabdi rumbuye. Jabdi i mena Jera e gha uu t…®ne, na iye Juda le wabwi loloniye regha.   
\p
\v 2 Josuwa i variyeŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru vavana th…® ri Jeriko na th…® wa Ai. Ghembake iyake ina Betel boimaniyeko, ghemba reghava idae Bet Aven ghadidiye. Josuwa i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúHu wa na vohu kelaŇča ŇčgoroŇčga thelauna gha ghawo.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča vama veth…® vakathavao iyako,  
\v 3 th…® njogha na th…® utu giya weya Josuwa, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa ghemba lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiye. Ma val…®kaiwae taulagh…®ke ghinda vara gaith…®we. Mbema u variyeŇčgi eŇčge tu o t…®ri tausan gh…®mogh…®moru na veth…® gaith…®we.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Iya kaiwae mbe t…®ri tausan eŇčge th…® raka na veth…® gaith…® Ai, ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® Ai e t…®ne th…® kivwalaŇčgi na th…® raka vo njogha e ghereinji.  
\v 5 Gh…®mogh…®moru Ai e t…®ne th…® vagegeŇčgi e ghembako gha ghamba ruru, na th…® raka njoŇča yamwa var…®var…®ye na th…® gaboŇčgiya Isirel ragagaith…® theto na theghewona. E mbaŇčako iyako Isirel ragagaith…®ko ma e lenji vur…®gheghe na th…® vo weinji lenji mararu.   
\p
\v 6 Amba Josuwa i mwana thethe gha kwama na i dipoumu e thelauko vwatae Ňčgora \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Dageraweko gha Bogis ghadidiye, na mbe Ňčgora vara iyako ghaghad yegh…®yegh…®ye. Isirel giyagiyaniye vambe th…® vakathava Ňčgoreiye na th…® mban…®yatha vugha e umbal…®nji. Lenji vakathako va i woraŇčgiya lenji nuwathar…®ko.  
\v 7 Kaero Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúOo, \nd Giya Loi\nd* vur…®vur…®ghegheniye! Buda kaiwae vara na menda u vaŇčgu valawaime Jor…®dan val…®mbwake? Menda u vakatha iyako na u vaŇčgu giyaime weŇčgiya Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® mukuwoime? Oo, ThoŇčgo mbema menda wo ya yaku eŇčge Jor…®dan val…®mbwa i lawalawaoko!  
\v 8 O \nd Giya Loi\nd*, ŇčgoroŇčga ne yaŇča? Lama ragagaith…®ke kaero menda th…® rakavo weŇčgiya ghama rath…®gh…®yako.  
\v 9 Kenan ghar…®ghar…®niye na vanautumake iyake ghar…®ghar…®niye wolagh…®ye ne th…® loŇčwa iyake utuniye, amba th…® raka mena th…® gabovaoime. Ne u vakatha budakai na idan mbe i lagh…®lagh…®ye vara?‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Isirel lenji thar…®  
\p
\v 10 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúU yondo vir…®! U vakatha budakai iya u dipoumu e thelauna vwatae?  
\v 11 Isirel menda th…® vakatha thar…®. Mava th…® ghambugha lo mbaro va ya dage weŇčgi Jeriko kaiwae, yaŇča mbaŇča ne hu ru Jeriko e t…®ne, hu mukuwo bigibigiko wolagh…®ye, ko iyemaeŇčge mendava th…® mbana vavana. Mendava th…® kwan na th…® mban…®Ňčgiya bigibigike thiyake vavana na th…® thuwoleŇčgi e lenji bigibigiko t…®net…®nenji.  
\v 12 Isirel tembe ghanjimberegha menda th…® vakatha ghanjivuyowo, iya kaiwae ma val…®kaiwanji menda th…® ndeghath…® vur…®gheghe na th…® gaith…® njogha weŇčgiya ghanji rath…®gh…®yako, mbema th…® raka vo eŇčge. Ma tembene ya thalavuŇčgava ghaghad ne hu mukuwo bigibigina wolagh…®ye iya va ya dageten…®na e ghemi, ko iyemaeŇčge menda hu mban…®Ňčgi.   
\p
\v 13 ‚ÄúU wa vo dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®na th…® vanamwe riwanji ghanjimberegha na th…® vivatha th…® raka mena e ghino evole mbaŇčambaŇča. Vo dage weŇčgi ghino, \nd Giya Loi\nd* Isirel lenji Loi, yaŇča, ‚ÄėIsirel ghar…®ghar…®niye, va ya dage e ghemi na hu mukuwo bigibigiko wolagh…®ye Jeriko e t…®ne. Ko iyemaeŇčge hu mban…®Ňčgiya bigibigiko thiyako vavana, iyava yaŇčake hu mukuwoŇčgi. Hu bigiyathuŇčgi ambane val…®kaiwami hu ndeghath…® vur…®gheghe na hu kivwalaŇčgiya ghami th…®gh…®yako.‚Äô  
\v 14 U dage weŇčgi na evole mbaŇčambaŇča ne th…® rakamena e (Dageraweko gha Bogis) ghadidiye e wabwi regha na regha. The wabwi ne (ya tuthi) \nd Giya Loi\nd* i tuthi, uu na uu th…® raka raŇčgi e wabwiko t…®ne, the uu \nd Giya Loi\nd* i tuthi amaamala na lenji ŇčgaŇčga/gha yayaoko ghar…®ghar…®niye ne th…® raka raŇčgi e uuko t…®ne; the amala \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i tuthi amaamalako na lenji ŇčgaŇčga/ghanjiyayao ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji ne i raŇčgi  
\v 15 amalana iyana kaero i (th…®) vaidi mukuwoko bigibiginiye vavana inawe ne i mare, weiyaŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga/gha yayaoko bigibiginiyeko wolagh…®ye, kaiwae kaero i womena monjina lagh…®ye Isirel weŇčgi na i raka lo mbaro.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 I gh…®viyava, vambe mbaŇčambaŇča moli Josuwa kaero i kula vathaŇčgiya Isirel th…® raka mena e wabwi na wabwi, na uu regha iya th…® mena \nd Giya Loi\nd* e ghamwae, na i ghatha raŇčgiya Juda gha wabwi.  
\v 17 Josuwa i kula vathaŇčgiya Juda gha wabwiko, na uu regha iya th…® raka raŇčgi, na uuko e t…®nenji \nd Giya Loi\nd* i ghatha raŇčgiya Jera gha uu. Josuwa kaero i kula vathaŇčgiva Jera gha uu e t…®ne amaamala na lenji ŇčgaŇčga; na amala regha iya na le ŇčgaŇčga th…® raka na \nd Giya Loi\nd* i ghatha raŇčgiya Jabdi na le ŇčgaŇčga.  
\v 18 Josuwa mbowo i kula vathaŇčgiva Jabdi le ŇčgaŇčga na amaamala regha iya i raŇčgi, na \nd Giya Loi\nd* i ghatha Eikan iye Kami nariye na Jabdi rumbuye.   
\p
\v 19 Amba Josuwa i dage weya Eikan iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčgu, u wovavwenyevwenyeŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd*, iye Isirel lenji Loi, na u tarawe. U utu giyama e ghino budakai mendava u vakatha. Ne u nderavunyivunyiya bigi regha e ghino.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Eikan i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru, kaero mendava ya vakatha thar…® \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Isirel lenji Loi e marae. Thar…®ke va ya vakathake iyake:  
\v 21 MbaŇča mukuwoko e t…®ne, ya thuwa kwama thovuye regha i mena Babilon, silva le vuyovuyowo mbala vama i wo paeb paun (pound), na gol vuvura le vuyovuyowo i kivwala wan paun (pound). Va mbema th…® wo vara nuwaŇčgu, iya kaiwae va ya mban…®Ňčgi. Ne vohu vaidiŇčgi elo Ňčgoloko t…®ne, va ya beku na silva ve ghena bode.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Amba Josuwa i variyeŇčgiya ravarivariye vavana, th…® ruku na i wa Eikan ele Ňčgoloko, na veth…® vaidi Ňčgoreiya me le utuma weŇčgi. Silva va ina bode.  
\v 23 Th…® bigi raŇčgiya e yaŇčathowathowako na th…® bigi wa weya Josuwa na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko weŇčgi, na th…® bigirawe \nd Giya Loi\nd* e ghamwae.   
\p
\v 24 Amba Josuwa weiyaŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko th…® vaŇčgwa Eikan, th…® mbana silvako, kwamako, gol…®ko, weiyaŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga, oyawarumbuye, le burumwaka, le doŇč…®ki, le sip, le Ňčgoloko, na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye e gha yayaoko t…®ne. Amba th…® yotakoŇčgi e gunugu idae Gunugu Vuyowo.  
\v 25 Na gheko Josuwa i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae menda u womena vuyowoke iyake weinda? E mbaŇčake iyake \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i womena vuyowoke iyake e ghen.‚ÄĚ Amba ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® tagavamara Eikan e var…®var…®, na tembe th…® tagavamareŇčgiva le ŇčgaŇčgako na le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye na th…® ŇčambuŇčgi.  
\v 26 Th…® wabwi vatha var…®var…® Eikan e vwatae, na noroke mbe inawe. Iya kaiwae val…®vaŇčgako iyako mbe idae vara Gunugu Vuyowo.  
\p \nd Giya Loi\nd* ma tembe i ghare gaith…®va weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.   
\c 8  
\s1 Isirel th…® wo Ai na th…® mukuwo  
\p
\v 1 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúTha u mararu, na tha u gharelagh…®lagh…®. U takoŇčgiya len ragagaith…®na wolagh…®ye, hu raka voro na vohu gaith…® Ai. Kaero ya vaŇčgura Ai gha kiŇč e n…®man ghare, weiyaŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®ko, ghambaeko na le thelauko ne ghen…®we.  
\v 2 Ne u vakatha weya Ai na gha kiŇč…®ko Ňčgora va u vakatha weya Jeriko na gha kiŇč, ko iyemaeŇčge e mbaŇčake iyake val…®kaiwami hu mbana bigibiginiyeko, na thetheghan ghemi regha na regha kaiwami. U vaŇčgu thuwoleŇčgiya len ragagaith…®na vavana e ghembana ghereiye, mbala hu vathin…®na gharenji na th…® munje th…® rakaraŇčgi gaith…® kaiwae, amba len ragagaith…®na e ghembana ghereiye th…® raka raŇčgi na th…® gaith…®.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 3 Kaero Josuwa i vivatha na i voro weiyaŇčgiya le ragagaith…®ko na veth…® gaith…® Ai. I gatha raŇčgiyaŇčgiya le ragagaith…® yamwa lenji ghanaghanagha teti tausan (30,000) na i variye yathuŇčgi gougouko iyako,  
\v 4 na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu vandeŇče wagiyawe. Huya kubaro e ghembana val…®vaŇčga, ko thava bwagabwaga moli, na mbe hu vivatha gaith…® kaiwae.  
\v 5 Ghino na ragagaith…®ke wolagh…®ye iya weiŇčguyaŇčgike mbene wo raka voro vara e ghembako, na mbaŇča ragagaith…® e ghembako ne th…® gaith…® weime Ňčgora va th…® vakathama, ne wo raka vo.  
\v 6 Mbala th…® renuwaŇča na thiŇčava, ‚ÄėIsirel ragagaith…®ko th…® rakavo weinda Ňčgora va th…® vakathama.‚Äô Ne th…® raka mbeleime, ne wo vakathaŇčgi na th…® raka iteta ghembana.  
\v 7 Ko amba ghemi ghami dauya vara iyako hu raka raŇčgi e lemi ghamba kubarona, na hu wo ghembana. Giya la Loi ne i wogiya e ghemi.  
\v 8 MbaŇča ne hu rakaru e ghembana t…®ne, hu woŇčambu, Ňčgora \nd Giya Loi\nd* va le renuwaŇča. Hu ghambugha iya ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke iyake.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Kaero Josuwa i variye yathuŇčgiya ragagaith…®ma, na mbowo veth…® roroghagha Ňčgora lenji ghamba kubaroko ‚ÄĒ Ai e yalasiniyeko, Ai na Betel ghanjilughawoghawo. Josuwa va mbowo i roghenava e kiyamuko gougouko iyako.   
\p
\v 10 I gh…®viyava ‚ÄĒ mbe mbaŇčambaŇča Josuwa kaero i thuweiru na i kula vathaŇčgiya ragagaith…®ko wolagh…®ye. Amba amalagh…®niye weiyayaŇčgiya Isirel lenji randevivako, th…® viva weŇčgiya ragagaith…®ko na veth…® gaith…® Ai.  
\v 11 Mbe th…® loŇčga gh…®dagh…®daŇča vara ghamba ruko lagh…®ye e ghembako t…®ne na th…® vakatha lenji kiyamu e ghaiwabuniyeko na gunugu ina Ai na thiye ghanji lughawoghawo.  
\v 12 Josuwa vambe i wabwivathava le ragagaith…® lenji ghanaghanagha paeb tausan (5,000) na thiya kubaro Ai e yalasiniyeko, Ai na Betel e ghanji lughawoghawo.  
\v 13 Josuwa i ghatha vakatha le ragagaith…®ko gaith…® kaiwae ‚ÄĒ wabwi lagh…®yeniye va inanji e ghembako ghaiwabuniye na vavanako e yalasiniyeko. Josuwa ghamberegha va mbowo njoghava e lenji kiyamu gougouko iyako, Jor…®dan e malamoniye.   
\p
\v 14 MbaŇča Ai gha kiŇč i thuweŇčgiya Isirel lenji ragagaith…®ko, mbema ghe na n…®ma eŇčge weiyaŇčgiya le ragagaith…® th…® raka raŇčgi na ghamwanji i ghembeya Jor…®dan, Ňčgora va th…® gaith…®kaima weinjiyaŇčgiya Isirel ragagaith…®. Ko iyemaeŇčge mava i ghareghare ragagaith…®ko e ghembako ghereiye ne th…® gaboŇčgi.  
\v 15 Josuwa na le ragagaith…®ko mbema th…® kwan…® eŇčge, th…® ruku na i ghembeya njamnjam…®ko th…® munjeva mbala ghanji rath…®gh…®yako th…®Ňča kaero meth…® kivwalaŇčgi.  
\v 16 Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye Ai e t…®ne, thavala val…®kaiwanji gaith…®, th…® raka raŇčgi na tembe th…® raka mbeleŇčgiva Josuwa na le ragagaith…®ko na i vakatha vama ghanji lughawoghawo lagh…®ye weya ghembako.  
\v 17 Gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye Ai na Betel e t…®nenji kaero th…® raka raŇčgivao na th…® iteta ghembako. Ghembako ghamba ruruko va i mavura na, ma tembe ragagaith…® regha inaweva na i rogaith…®ten.   
\p
\v 18 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúU wo len gaith…®na gha kin na maraena i ghembeya Ai; kaero ya worawa ghemba e n…®man…®na ghare.‚ÄĚ Josuwa i vakatha Ňčgora \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i dagewe,  
\v 19 na mbaŇčaniye vara Josuwa i vakatha iyako, ragagaith…®ma va thiya kubaroma th…® yondovir…®, mbema ghenji na n…®manji eŇčge th…® rakaru na th…® wo ghembako, na th…® woŇčambu.   
\p
\v 20 Ai ragagaith…® veth…® gaith…® matav…® na maranji i njogha, amba th…® thuweya mundu i voro e Ňčgal…®l…®ko. Ma tembe kamwath…® reghava na val…®kaiwanji th…® vo reŇčawe, kaiwae Isirel ragagaith…® iya va th…® rakavo na i ghembeya Jor…®dan njamnjamniyeko, th…® raka matav…® amba th…® gaboŇčgi.  
\v 21 MbaŇča Josuwa na le ragagaith…®ko va th…® thuweya munduko th…® ghareghare lenji val…®ragagaith…®ma kaero meth…® wo ghembako, th…® raka matav…® eŇčge kaero th…® ghene Ňčgoruru Ai lenji ragagaith…®ko.  
\v 22 Isirel lenji ragagaith…® va inanji e ghembako t…®ne th…® raka na i ghembeŇčgiya Ai ragagaith…®, iya kaiwae kaero inanji vara Isirel ragagaith…® wabwi theghewo e ghanji lughawoghawo, na ma tembe val…®kaiwaeva Ai le ragagaith…® regha i vo raŇčgi e yawayawaliye. Th…® gabovaoŇčgi na iko.  
\v 23 Vambe Ai gha kiŇč ghamberegha eŇčge e yawayawaliye. Ragagaith…®ko th…® yalawe na veth…® vaŇčgugiya weya Josuwa.   
\p
\v 24 Isirel mbema th…® gabovaoŇčgi vara ghanji rath…®gh…®yako Jor…®dan malamoniye e t…®ne, ko amba th…® raka njogha Ai na tembe th…® gabovaoŇčgiva thavala va inanji gheko.  
\v 25 Ai ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji ghanaghanagha tuwel tausan (12,000) gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau.  
\v 26 Josuwa mava i wonjaniya gaith…®ko gha kin, vambe inawe vara e n…®mae ghaghad va th…® mukuwoŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye va thiya yaku gheko.  
\v 27 Ko iyemaeŇčge Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® takoŇčgiya thetheghan na the bigibigiva va th…® mban…®Ňčgi mbe thiye kaiwanji. Iyako \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i dage weya Josuwa na th…® vakatha.  
\v 28 Josuwa va i woŇčambwa Ai. Ghembako mbe ina vara e mukuwo t…®ne ghaghad noroke iya ya roriya riuriuniyeke.  
\v 29 Josuwa iŇča na th…® tagavamara Ai gha kiŇč na th…® wovakwata riwae e umbwa ghaghad yegh…®yegh…®ye. Vama Ňčgoreiya tauya wovoŇčgu, iŇča na ragagaith…®ko veth…® wokiyathu e ghembako ghamba ruru na th…® variya riwaeko e var…®var…® ‚ÄĒ wabwi lagh…®ye moli. Var…®var…®ko gha wabwiko vambe i nawe mbaŇča th…® roriya riuriuke iyake.   
\s1 Th…® mbaro e Ou Ibol  
\p
\v 30-31 MbaŇča vavana e ghereiye Josuwa na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye veth…® raka voro e Ou Ibol. MbaŇča veth…® raka vutha gheko Josuwa i dage weŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruko vavana iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vatada ghamba vowo weya Giya la Loi. Hu vatad…® Ňčgoreiye vavaghare ina Mosese ele Mbaro t…®ne. Mosese, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo va iŇča, ghambavowo gha vatavatad…® ne hu vatad…® e var…®var…® ma th…® ten…®Ňčgi na th…® vanamwe ghad…®d…®nji e aiyan.‚ÄĚ Amba th…® vatada ghamba vowoma. Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® giya lenji vowo thetheghan mbwanambwanaŇčgi weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* na th…® Ňčambu vaoŇčgi, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva th…® vowoŇča v…®ghath…® vowoniyewe.  
\v 32 Gheko, Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye e maranji Josuwa i rori valawe Mosese le Mbaroko iyava i rori e var…®var…® va i vanamwe ghanji yamoyamo.  
\v 33 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® mevathavatha na th…® ndeghath…® e wabwi theghewo, weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji randevivaŇčgi, rambarombaro, raghathaghatha na bwabwari thiya ndeghath…® e wabwiko theghewoko t…®nenji, na Dagerawe gha Bogis ina e ghanji lughawoghawo. Wabwi regha iya vaŇčga na vaŇčga na Dagerawe gha Bogis ina e ghanji lughawoghawo. Wabwi regha ghereinji i ghemba Ou Ibol na regha ghereinji i ghembeya Ou Gerijim. Livai le wabwi e t…®ne, ravowovowoko th…® ndekewa Dagerawe gha Bogis na th…® ndeghath…® e lenji ghamba ndeghath…® vaŇčga na vaŇčga. \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo, Mosese va i dage na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye iyako, mbaŇča ne th…® mena na th…® wo ghanji dagemwaewo.   
\p
\v 34 Josuwa ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye, i vaona Mbaroko wolagh…®ye e gha buk t…®ne, iya va i utuŇča dagemwaewoko na gurako Ňčgoreiye va th…® rorinjoŇča Mbaroko e gha buk t…®ne.  
\v 35 Josuwa i vaonavao mbaroko wolagh…®ye Mosese va i rori njoŇča, weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye, weŇčgiya wanakau, gamagai na bwabwari iyava thiya yaku e t…®nenjiko.   
\c 9  
\s1 Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® valogha Josuwa nuwa  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča kiŇč…®Ňčgiko wolagh…®ye inanji Jor…®dan e yalasiniyeko, th…® loŇčwa Isirel lenji vur…®gheghe utuniye weinjiyaŇčgiya Ai na Jeriko ‚ÄĒ thiye th…® yakuŇča bobokuluko vwatavwatanji, thiye inanji e bobokuluko r…®gher…®ghenji, na thiye thiya roŇčgalai Njigh…® Meditareiniyan ghadidiye na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva kiŇč…®Ňčgi inanji e ghaiwabuko vewo Lebenon ‚ÄĒ kiŇč…®Ňčgike thiyake ghar…®ghar…® wabwike thiyake lenji kiŇč…®Ňčgi ‚ÄĒ Hiti, Amori, Kenani, Perisi, Hivi na Jebusi.  
\v 2 KiŇč…®Ňčgike thiyake th…® wabwi vathavathaŇčgi lenji ragagaith…® na regha na lenji r…®ghe regha ‚ÄĒ nuwanjiya th…® kivwalaŇčgiya Josuwa na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.   
\p
\v 3 Ko iyemaeŇčge, mbaŇča Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye, thiye Hivi, th…® loŇčwe budakai Josuwa va i vakatha weŇčgiya Jeriko na Ai,  
\v 4 iwaeŇčge nuwanjiya th…® valogha nuwae. Kaero th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiyake: th…® mbana ghan…®Ňčga e begibegi teteuye th…® bigi vala doŇč…®ki e vwatavwatanji weiye waen varivariye tembe teteuyeva na th…® Ňčgiya valevaleweŇčgi.  
\v 5 Ghar…®ghar…®ko tembe th…® njimboŇčgiva kwamakwama teteuye na gheghenji ghae teteuye th…® Ňčgiya valevaleweŇčgi. Na bred va th…® mban kaero i vur…®gheghe na i wado.  
\v 6 Amba ravarivariyeko thiya wareri th…® raka weŇčgiya Josuwa na Isirel gh…®mogh…®moruniye inanji e lenji kiyamu Gilgal e t…®ne, na veth…® dage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo raka mena e vanautuma bwagabwaga moli. Nuwameiya hu vakatha dagerawe regha weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Isirel gh…®mogh…®moruniye th…® dage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae na ne wo vakatha dagerawe e ghemi? Mbwata mbema hu yaku evasiwameke.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Th…® dage weya Josuwa th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhime len rakakaiwo.‚ÄĚ  
\p Ko iyemaeŇčge Josuwa i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThavala ghemi na aŇčga hu raka mena?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Th…® gonjoghawe e riuriuke iyake, ‚ÄúWo raka mena e vanautuma bwagabwaga moli amalana, kaiwae kaero wo loŇčwa Giya lemi Loi le vakathana utuniye. Kaerova wo loŇčwa bigibigike wolagh…®ye va i vakathaŇčgi Ijipt e t…®ne  
\v 10 na budakai va i vakatha weŇčgiya Amori lenji kiŇč theghewo Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro ‚ÄĒ KiŇč Saihon, Hesbon gha kiŇč na KiŇč Og, Basan gha kiŇč va i yaku Astarot.  
\v 11 Iya kaiwae lama randevivaŇčgi na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye thiya yaku e vanautumako iyako t…®ne th…® dage weime th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėHu mbana ghan…®Ňčga lemi loŇčgaloŇčgana kaiwae. Vohu vutha weŇčgi na hu utu weimiyaŇčgi huŇča, ‚ÄúGhime lemi rakakaiwo. Hu vakatha dagerawe weime.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô  
\v 12 Wo hu thuwa ghama bred…®ke. MbaŇča mendava wo iteta ghemba na wo mena wo thuweŇčga, vamba i dade vara. Ko wo hu thuwe! Kaero i vur…®gheghe na i wado.  
\v 13 MbaŇča va wo guduŇčgiya waen…®ke varivariye, vambe totogha vara. Ko wo hu thuwe! Kaero th…® mamaviya. Ghama kwamakwamake na ghegheme ghae kaero th…® teteuye kaiwae gh…®naghake molao moli.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 14 Isirel gh…®mogh…®moruniye vavana th…® mbana ghan…®Ňčgama vavana na th…® ghan, ko iyemaeŇčge mava th…® vaito gha rumwaru weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.  
\v 15 Josuwa i vakatha v…®ghath…® gha dagerawe weiyaŇčgiya Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niyeko, amba i variye yathuŇčgi. Wabwi Isirel ghanjigiyagiya th…® tholo na th…® vikiki ghath…®gha dageraweko iyako.   
\s1 Isirel th…® loŇčwe vaidi Gibiyon mendava th…® yaroŇčgi  
\p
\v 16 MbaŇča thegheto e ghereiye Isirel th…® loŇčwe vaidi Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® yaroŇčgi, ko mbema th…® yaku vara evasiwanji.  
\v 17 Amba Isirel th…® raka iteta Gilgal na thiya wareri. MbaŇča thegheto e ghereiye kaero veth…® raka vutha e ghembaghembako iya ghar…®ghar…®ko va thiya yakuwe. E ghembaghembake thiyake: Gibiyon, Kepira, Biyarot, na Kiriyat Jeyarim.  
\v 18 Ko iyemaeŇčge Isirel mava th…® gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako, kaiwae lenji rambarombaroko kaero mendava th…® tholo \nd Giya Loi\nd* Isirel lenji Loi e idae.  
\p Isirel wabwiko lagh…®ye th…® liya rambarombaroko ghanjiutu lenji vakathako iyako kaiwae.  
\v 19 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® dage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKaero mendava wo tholo \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Isirel lenji Loi e idae. MbaŇčake ma val…®kaiwae ra vakatha v…®r…® weŇčgi.  
\v 20 Ra viyathuŇčgi kaiwae kaero mendava wo dagarawe weŇčgi, kaiwae thoŇčgo ra gaboŇčgi, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le ghatemuru ne i nja weinda.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 Th…® gotubwe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúHu viyathuŇčgi mbe thiya yaku, ko ne th…® tabo eŇčge nd…®ghe gha rageth…®Ňčgi na mbwa gha raguduŇčgi, Isirel taulagh…®ke kaiwanda.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae rambarombaroko lenji dagerawe i mboromboro.   
\p
\v 22 Josuwa iŇča na th…® vaŇčgu menaŇčgiya Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye weya amalagh…®niye na i vaitoŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae va hu mena hu kwan…®yaroime, huŇča, hu raka mena e vanautuma bwagabwaga moli, thela i wo mbema hu yaku vara evasiwame.  
\v 23 MbaŇčake kaero Loi i guraŇčga. MbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ne hu geth…®getha nd…®ghe na hu guduguda mbwa Isirel lenji Loi le Ňčgolo kaiwae.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 Th…® gonjogha weya Josuwa th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, mendava wo vakatha iyana, kaiwae kaerova wo loŇčwe emunjoru moli, Giya len Loi kaerova i dagera weya le rakakaiwo Mosese, ne i gabovaoŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye na i wogiya thelauke lagh…®ye e ghemi. Va wo rerenuwaŇča lagh…®ye moli yawal…®me kaiwae, wo mararu iya kaiwae va wo vakatha iyana.  
\v 25 Kaero iname e n…®man ghare mbaŇčake. U vakatha weime the bigi u renuwaŇča i rumwaru e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 Iya kaiwae Josuwa i dage ten…®Ňčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye na thava th…® gaboŇčgi.  
\v 27 E mbaŇčako vara iyako Josuwa i vakatha Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® tabo rakakaiwobwaga. Th…® geth…®getha nd…®ghe na th…® guduguda mbwa wabwi Isirel kaiwanji na \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Ňčgolo, ghamba vowoko kaiwae Ňčgoreiye \nd Giya Loi\nd* i tuthi ne veth…® kururuwe. Mbe th…® vakavakatha vara iyake ghaghad noroke.   
\c 10  
\iex Jos 10:6‚Äď23:11 Ghenjelawa i mena Panorama we  
\iex Amba Josuwa na Isirel th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgi Kenan e val…®vaŇčga regha na regha e vanautumako t…®ne. Th…® gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® gheko, ko iyemaeŇčge th…® ghakuŇčgiya vavana na th…® yaku weiŇčgiyaŇčgi.  
\iex Amba Josuwa i tagaviyaviya thelauko, Isirel gha uu regha na regha kaiwanji. Th…® raka e tomethi val…®vaŇčgaŇčgi na veth…® yakuŇča ghembaghemba Kenan va th…® vakathaŇčgi. Theghathegha lemoya e ghereiye amba Josuwa i takovathavathaŇčgiva Isirel na regha.  
\s1 Isirel i kivwalaŇčgi Amori  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Adoni-Sedek i loŇčwe vaidi Josuwa kaero mendava i wo Ai na i mukuwo na i tagavamare gha kiŇč, Ňčgoreiya va i vakatha weya Jeriko na gha kiŇč. Na tembe i loŇčweva Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® vakatha dagerawe na th…® vanevane weinjiyaŇčgi na thiya yaku e t…®nenji.  
\v 2 IwaeŇčge amalagh…®niye na le ghar…®ghar…® Jerusalem e t…®ne gharenji iyo lagh…®ye moli kaiwae Gibiyon iye ghemba lagh…®ye na i kivwalaŇčgi ghembaghemba va inanji gheko, na vambe i lagh…®ye kivwalava Ai, na gha ragagaith…®ko va th…® thovuyeŇča gaith…®.  
\v 3 Kaero Adoni-Sedek i variye totoke iyake weŇčgiya KiŇč Hoham Hebron gha kiŇč, KiŇč Piram Jamut gha kiŇč, KiŇč Japiya Lakis gha kiŇč, na KiŇč Debi Eglon gha kiŇč,  
\v 4 iŇča, ‚ÄúHu raka mena hu thalavuŇčgo na vara gaith…® Gibiyon, kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® e ghembako iyako kaero mendava th…® vakatha vanevane yakuyakuniye weinjiyaŇčgi Josuwa na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 5 Amba Amori gha kiŇč…®Ňčgi theghelimake thiyake: Jerusalem gha kiŇč, Hebron gha kiŇč, Jamut gha kiŇč, Lakis gha kiŇč, na Eglon gha kiŇč, lenji ragagaith…®ko th…® wabwi na regha na veth…® raka vagh…®liya Gibiyon na th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgi.   
\p
\v 6 Iyako kaiwae Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® variye toto i wawe Josuwa e lenji kiyamuko Gilgal e t…®ne. Totoko iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, kaiwae kaero wo tabona lemi rakakaiwo, mbaŇčake nuwameiya u thalavuime, na thava hu viyathuime. Amori lenji kiŇč…®Ňčgi, e vanautumako iya bobokuluko lemoyowe, kaero menda th…® wabwi na regha na th…® raka mena th…® gaith…® weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Kaero Josuwa na le ragagaith…®ko wolagh…®ye, na le ragagaith…® thovuthovuye, thiya wareri Gilgal na th…® raka voro gheko.  
\v 8 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe Josuwa, iŇča, ‚ÄúThava u mararuŇčgi. Kaero ya takoraweŇčgi e n…®man ghare. Ma tembe reghava val…®kaiwae ne i gaith…® njogha e ghen.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Gougouko iyako Josuwa na le ragagaith…® th…® rakari Gilgal na veth…® raka vutha Gibiyon. Kaiwae Amori lenji ragagaith…®ko mava e lenji ghareghare mun, gharenji va iyo mbaŇča Isirel th…® raka vutha na th…® gaith…® weŇčgi.  
\v 10 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakathaŇčgi Amori th…® gharelagh…®lagh…® lagh…®ye mbaŇča th…® thuweŇčgi Isirel ragagaith…®ko th…® gaith…® weŇčgi. Isirel ragagaith…®ko th…® gaboŇčgi vavana Gibiyon ele val…®vaŇčga na th…® mbeleŇčgi th…® raka njoŇča ou Bet Horon ghadidiye na mbe th…® mbelekikiŇčgi vara e yaghalako na veth…® ghad Ajeka na Makeda.  
\v 11 MbaŇča va e lenji voko t…®ne weŇčgi Isirel ragagaith…® na th…® raka njoŇča ouko ghadidiye, amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i birinjoŇča var…®var…® lagh…®lagh…®ye thiya dobu nja e buruburu na th…® gaboŇčgi ghaghad th…® rakavutha Ajeka. Var…®var…®ko va th…® gaboŇčgi ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo moli, i kivwala Isirel ragagaith…® va th…® gaboŇčgi.   
\p
\v 12 Va e mbaŇčako vara iya \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakathaŇčgi Isirel na th…® kivwalaŇčgi Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye, Isirel e maranji amba Josuwa i naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, iŇča,  
\q1 ‚ÄúVaraena, mbe u ndeghath…® vara Gibiyon e vwataena;  
\q1 Manjalana, tembe u ndeghath…®va e Malamo Aijalon vwata.‚ÄĚ   
\q1
\v 13 Iya kaiwae varaeko i ndeghath…® na manjalako tembe i ndeghath…®va, ghaghad Isirel th…® kivwalaŇčgi raghanjith…®gh…®yako.  
\m Utuutuke thiyake th…® rorinjogha e Buk idae Jasa. Varaeko va i ndeghath…® yamoe moli e buruburuko, na mava veronja vorivori, Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča regha le molamolao.  
\v 14 Va i vivako, noroke na i ghaoko ma tembe mbaŇča regha Ňčgoreiyeva iyako, mbaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* i thombeya mbema lolo eŇčge le naŇčgo Ňčgora iyako. Kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* vambe weiyaŇčgi vara Isirel na th…® gaith…®.   
\p
\v 15 Iyake e ghereiye amba Josuwa weiyaŇčgi Isirel th…® raka njogha e lenji kiyamu Gilgal e t…®ne.   
\s1 Th…® gaboŇčgi Amori lenji kiŇč…®Ňčgi theghelima  
\p
\v 16 IyemaeŇčge, Amori lenji kiŇč theghelima va th…® raka vo na vethiya kubaro e maŇčgavar…® Makeda e t…®ne.  
\v 17 MbaŇča Josuwa i loŇčwe vaidi kiŇč…®ke theghelima th…® kubaro e maŇčgavar…® na kaero meth…® vaidiŇčgi,  
\v 18 amba iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vabulale voreŇča var…®var…® lagh…®lagh…®ye vavana e maŇčgavar…®na ghae, na hu vaŇčguraweŇčgi ragat…®gat…® vavanawe.  
\v 19 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbe hu mbelekikiŇčgi vara iya ghami rath…®gh…®yana vavana. Thava hu viyathuŇčgi na vethiya vo ru e ghambaghambanji t…®nenji.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 20 Othembe Josuwa na Isirel ragagaith…® th…® gaboŇčgi ghanjiune lagh…®yeniye, ko iyemaeŇčge vaona lolo va vethiya vo ru e ghambaghambanji ghanji gana t…®nenji na ma val…®kaiwanji th…® gaboŇčgi.  
\v 21 Ragagaith…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® raka njoghawe Josuwa, ma regha mun i vaidi vuyowo e kiyamuko, Makeda e t…®ne. Ma tembe lolo reghava ghal…®Ňčae i ruuruu Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye weŇčgi.   
\p
\v 22 Amba Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúHu mwanathewo maŇčgavar…®na ghae, na hu vaŇčgu menaŇčgi kiŇč…®na theghelima weŇčgo.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 Kaero th…® vaŇčguwaŇčgi kiŇč…®ko theghelima weya Josuwa ‚ÄĒ Jerusalem gha kiŇč, Hebron gha kiŇč, Jamut gha kiŇč, Lakis gha kiŇč, na Eglon gha kiŇč.  
\v 24 MbaŇča veth…® vaŇčgugiyaŇčgi weya Josuwa, amba i kula vathaŇčgi Isirel gh…®mogh…®moruniyeko wolagh…®ye, na i dage weŇčgi ragagaith…®ko lenji randevivaŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúHu raka mena gheke na hu vuruvala e kiŇč…®Ňčgike thiyake numonumonji.‚ÄĚ Amba th…® raka raŇčgi na th…® vuruvala e numonumonji.   
\p
\v 25 Josuwa i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThava hu mararu na hu gharelagh…®lagh…®. Hu vur…®gheghe eŇčge na weimi lemi gharematuwo. Kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i vakatha Ňčgora iyake weŇčgi ghami rath…®gh…®yake wolagh…®ye iya mo hu gaith…®ko weimiyaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Kaero Josuwa iŇča na th…® gaboŇčgi kiŇč…®ko na th…® bigi kithoŇčgi e umbwaumbwa umbolima, na mbe th…® kwatekwate vara gheko ghaghad yegh…®yegh…®ye moli.   
\p
\v 27 Varae ve ronja amba Josuwa i dage weŇčgi na th…® biginjoŇča riwanjiko e umbwaumbwako na veth…® biriyathuŇčgi e maŇčgavar…®ma va thiya kubaromawe. E maŇčgavar…®ko ghae th…® bigirawe var…®var…® lagh…®lagh…®yewe, na mbe inanjiwe e mbaŇčake iyake.   
\p
\v 28 E mbaŇčako iyako Josuwa i wo ghemba Makeda na gha kiŇč. I gabovaoŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye na ma tembe reghava e yawayawaliye. Va i vakathawe Makeda gha kiŇč Ňčgora va i vakathawe Jeriko gha kiŇč.   
\s1 Josuwa i gaith…® weŇčgi Amori ghembaghembaniye vavanava  
\p
\v 29 Iyako e ghereiye, amba Josuwa na le ragagaith…® th…® raka na mbowo veth…® gaith…®va Lib…®na.  
\v 30 \nd Giya Loi\nd* vamba i wogiyava ghembako iyako weŇčgi Isirel. Ghembako ghar…®ghar…®niye wolagh…®ye va th…® gabovaoŇčgi, ma tembe reghava e yawayawaliye. Na va th…® vakathawe gha kiŇč…®ko Ňčgoreiye va th…® vakathawe Jeriko gha kiŇč.   
\p
\v 31 Iyake e ghereiye, Josuwa na le ragagaith…® th…® raka itete Lib…®na na th…® raka Lakis. Th…® raka vagh…®liya ghembako iyako amba th…® gaith…®we.  
\v 32 MbaŇča theghewoniye e t…®ne, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i wora ghemba Lakis, Isirel e n…®manji ghare. Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghembako t…®ne th…® gabovaoŇčgi Ňčgora va th…® vakatha weŇčgi Lib…®na ghar…®ghar…®niye.  
\v 33 IyemaeŇčge Horam, Geja gha kiŇč i voroma na i munjeva i thalavuŇčgi Lakis, ko iyemaeŇčge Josuwa i kivwalaŇčgi weiyaŇčgi le ragagaith…® ‚ÄĒ i gabovaoŇčgi na ma tembe reghava e yawayawaliye.   
\p
\v 34 Josuwa na le ragagaith…® th…® raka itete Lakis na veth…® gaith…® Eglon. Th…® raka vutha th…® ndevagh…®liya na th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgi.  
\v 35 Va e mbaŇčako iyako th…® kivwalaŇčgi na th…® gabovaoŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye, Ňčgora va th…® vakatha weŇčgi ghemba Lakis.   
\p
\v 36 Josuwa na le ragagaith…® th…® raka itete Eglon na th…® raka voro e bobokuluŇčgi na veth…® raka vutha Hebron, amba th…® gaith…® gheko  
\v 37 na th…® kivwalaŇčgi. Th…® un…®gh…® gha kiŇč na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghembako iyako, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji. Ma tembe th…® iteteva lolo regha e yawayawaliye. Th…® vakatha Ňčgora meth…® vakatha Eglon e t…®ne.   
\p
\v 38 Josuwa na le ragagaith…® th…® raka vagh…®le na th…® gaith…® weŇčgi Debi,  
\v 39 th…® kivwalaŇčgi weiye gha kiŇč na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwaeva. Th…® gabovaoŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye. Josuwa va i vakathawe Debi na gha kiŇč Ňčgora va i vakatha weŇčgi Hebron na Lakis ghanji kiŇč…®Ňčgi.   
\p
\v 40-41 Kenani yaghalaniye, val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye iyako, Josuwa na le ragagaith…® kaero th…® wo. Th…® kivwalaŇčgi kiŇč…®ko iya th…® mbaroŇčaŇčgi ghembaghemba e bobokuluko vanautumaniye: vuruvuru vwatavwatae e yaghalako, bobokulu malamoniyeŇčgi, e yalasiko, na bobokuluko ghadighadidiji val…®vaŇčga e boimako. Josuwa i viva weŇčgi le ragagaith…®ko Kades Baniya e t…®ne e yaghalako, ghaghad Gaja e njigh…® ghadidiye. Va i viva weŇčgi Gosen ele val…®vaŇčga na ve wo Gibiyon e ghaiwabuko.  
\v 42 Josuwa va i kivwalaŇčgi kiŇč…®Ňčgiko na lenji ghamba mbaroko e mbaŇčako iyako. Va val…®kaiwae i vakatha iyako kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Isirel lenji Loi, va i gaith…® le ghar…®ghar…®ko kaiwanji.   
\p
\v 43 Iyako e ghereiye amba Josuwa na le ragagaith…®ko th…® raka njogha e lenji kiyamu Gilgal e t…®ne.   
\c 11  
\s1 Josuwa i kivwalaŇčgi ghaiwabuko gha kiŇč…®Ňčgi  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča Isirel lenji vur…®gheghe e gaith…®ko totoniye ve vuthawe KiŇč Jabim, Heijo e t…®ne, iwaeŇčge i variye utu i wawe KiŇč Jobab, Madon e t…®ne, na tembe i wa weŇčgiva kiŇč inanji Simiron na Ak…®sap,  
\v 2 na kiŇč vavanava inanji e bobokulu vanautumaniye, e ghaiwabuko, na i wa Jor…®dan e malamoniye, Galili e yaghalaniyeko e ououko r…®gher…®ghenji, na e ghembaghemba th…® roŇčgalai e njigh…® ghadidiye Dor ghadidiye.  
\v 3 Tembe i variyeva utu i wa weŇčgi Kenani ghar…®ghar…®niye inanji Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga na val…®vaŇčga, weiŇčgiya Amori, Hiti Perisi, Jebusi inanji e bobokulu vanautumaniye, na tembe i wa weŇčgiva Hivi inanji thiya yaku e Ou Hemon r…®ghe Mij…®pa ele val…®vaŇčga.  
\v 4 Th…® raka mena weinjiyaŇčgi lenji ragagaith…® lemoyo moli lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya kerakerako e njigh…®ko ghadidiye. Vavana va th…® rakatha e waŇčga momod…®Ňčgi na vavana thiya loŇčga.  
\v 5 KiŇč…®Ňčgike thiyake th…® wabwi vatha lenji ragagaith…®ko wolagh…®ye na regha na th…® kiyamu e mbwa idae Merom, amba th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgi Isirel.   
\p
\v 6 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúThava u mararuŇčgi, kaiwae ne Ňčgora vara iyake evole, Ghino \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne ya gabovaoŇčgi. Len ragaith…® ne th…® vakathaŇčgi lenji hos…®Ňčgi thiya kuvokuvo na th…® ŇčambuŇčgi lenji waŇčga momod…®na wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Kaero Josuwa na le ragagaith…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® raka veth…® vathin gharenji na th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgi e mbwa Merom.  
\v 8 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha Isirel na th…® kivwalaŇčgi e gaith…®ko. Th…® rakambeleŇčgi e ghaiwabuko ghaghad Misrepot Maim na Saidon, na i vorowoko e boimako ve wo gunugu idae Mij…®pa. Gaith…®ko vambe i mbele vara na ghanji rath…®yako na ko ma tembe reghava e yawayawaliye.  
\v 9 Josuwa i vakatha weŇčgi budakai \nd Giya Loi\nd* va le utumawe: i vakathaŇčgiya lenji hos…®ko thiya kuvokuvo na i ŇčambuŇčgiya lenji waŇčga momod…®ko wolagh…®ye.   
\p
\v 10 Va e mbaŇčako iyako Heijo gha kiŇč…®ko i mbaroŇča ghamba rothanavuko thiyako e vanautumako iyako. Vama th…® gaith…®vao e ghembaghembako thiyako amba Josuwa na le ragagaith…® th…® raka na veth…® gaith…® Heijo. Th…® wo ghembako iyako, th…® un…®gha gha kiŇč…®ko na  
\v 11 th…® gabovaoŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye, na th…® woŇčambu ghembako.   
\p
\v 12 Josuwa i mban…®vaoŇčgiya ghembaghembako thiyako na gha kiŇč…®Ňčgiko na i gabovaoŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye, Ňčgoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo Mosese va le utuutuwe.  
\v 13 IyemaeŇčge Isirel mava th…® ŇčambuŇčgiya ŇčgoloŇčgolo va th…® vatad…®Ňčgi Ňčgorava nja ghambae, ko mbe Heijo eŇčge Josuwa va i woŇčambu.  
\v 14 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® bigiŇčgiya bigibigi thovuthovuye e ghembaghembako iyako t…®nenji na thetheghan Ňčgora sip, burumwaka na gout, mbe thiye kaiwanji. Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye va th…® gabovaoŇčgi, ma tembe reghava e yawayawaliye th…® itete.  
\v 15 Budakai \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i utu giya weya le rakakaiwo Mosese, Mosese te vambe i utu valaweva Josuwa na i vakatha Ňčgoreiye. Josuwa va i ghambu na i vamboromboro \nd Giya Loi\nd* le renuwaŇča. Va i vakatha bigibigiko wolagh…®ye Mosese va i utu giyawe.   
\p
\v 16 Josuwa va i wo thelauko lagh…®ye iyako, ghamba mbaroŇčgike thiyake: vanautuma e bobokuluŇčgi na e ouou r…®gher…®ghenji, val…®vaŇčga ghaiwabuko na yaghalako, Gosen le val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye na vanautuma e vuruvuru vwatavwatae e yaghalako na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Jor…®dan malamoniye.  
\v 17 Vanautumako iya ve wo ou Halak val…®vaŇčga e yaghalako Idom ghadidiye, ve wo Baalgad e ghaiwabuko, Lebenon e malamoniye Ou Hemon e yaghalaniyeko.  
\v 18 Josuwa i gaith…® weiyaŇčgiya kiŇč…®Ňčgiko e vanautumako mbaŇča molao na i gabovaoŇčgi.  
\v 19 Mbe Gibiyon ghar…®ghar…®niye eŇčge vara th…® vakatha mal…®l…® yakuyakuniye gha dagerawe weinjiyaŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye. E ghembako iyako Hivi vavana inanjiwe. Ko ghembaghembako wolagh…®ye va th…® gaith…®we na th…® gabovaoŇčgi.  
\v 20 Iya vanautumake thiyake \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i vakatha th…® ghatemuru lagh…®ye na mbe th…® gaith…® vur…®gheghe vara weinjiyaŇčgiya Isirel ghaghadi Isirel th…® kivwalaŇčgi na th…® gabovaoŇčgi ma weinji mun lenji gharev…®r…® kaiwanji. Va th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye \nd Giya Loi\nd* le dagerawe weya Mosese.   
\p
\v 21 Josuwa vambe i mukuwoŇčgiva wabwi vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha idanji Anak. Wabwike iyake va thiya yaku e ghembaghembake thiyake ‚ÄĒ Hebron, Debi, Anab na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva vavana va inanji e ououko, e vanautuma Juda na Isirel t…®nenji. Josuwa va i mukuwoŇčgi na ghambaghambanjiko tembe Ňčgoreiyeva.  
\v 22 Ma tembe Anak reghava i yakuyaku e vanautumako iyako t…®ne, vambe gheviyeŇčge inanji thiya yaku Gaja, Gat na As…®dod.   
\p
\v 23 Josuwa i wo vanautumako lagh…®ye iyako, Ňčgoreiye \nd Giya Loi\nd* va le utuutu weya Mosese, ne i wogiya weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye ghambanji. Amba i tagaviyaviya thelauko na vuvura iya, uu regha iya e t…®nenjiko kaiwanji.  
\p E mbaŇčako iyako amba ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® towo e gaith…®.   
\c 12  
\s1 KiŇč…®Ňčgi Mosese va i kivwalaŇčgi  
\p
\v 1 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye kaerova th…® gaith…® na th…® kivwalaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® thiya yaku Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako, ve wo Anoni gunuguniye na i mena Jor…®dan gunuguniye na i wa e ghaiwabuko ve wo Ou Hemon. E val…®vaŇčgako iyako va th…® kivwalaŇčgiya kiŇč theghewo.  
\v 2 KiŇč…®ko regha idae Saihon, amalagh…®niye va i yaku Hesbon na i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye. Le ghambambaro i ri Aroer…®, ghembake iyake ina Anoni gunuguniye gha teghala, na i ri e gunuguko yamwae na vewo Walagh…®ta Jabok, Amon ghanji teghala, iyako Giliyad lenji thelau val…®mboro.  
\v 3 Le ghamba mbaroko ghaghad Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan gunuguniye val…®vaŇčga e boimako, i ri Njigh…® Galili e yaghalako na i wa Njigh…® Maremareniye. Tembe i mbaroŇčava thelauko iya Njigh…® Maremareniye e boimako, iri Bet Jesimot, e yaghalaniyeko, na ve wo Ou Pisga r…®ghe.   
\p
\v 4 Mosese na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye vambe, th…® kivwalava Basan lenji kiŇč ‚ÄĒ idae KiŇč Og. Iye va kiŇč vur…®vur…®ghegheniye na moumouniye wabwi Repa e t…®nenji. Va i mbaro weŇčgiya Astarot na Edrei.  
\v 5 KiŇč…®ke iyake va i mbaroŇča val…®vaŇčga ghaiwabuko ve wo Ou Hemon e boimako na ve wo ghemba idae Saleka. Va i mbaroŇča Basan le val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye na ve wo val…®vaŇčga e boimako ‚ÄĒ Gesu na Maka e lenji val…®vaŇčga. Le ghamba mbaroko mboro tembe ve wova Giliyad val…®vaŇčga e yaghalako ghaghad KiŇč Saihon ‚ÄĒ Hesbon lenji kiŇč gha ghad…®ko.   
\p
\v 6 KiŇč…®ke theghewoke thiyake Mosese na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® kivwalaŇčgi. Mosese, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo va i wogiya kiŇč…®ko lenji ghamba mbaroŇčgiko weŇčgiya wabwike thiyake: Rubin le wabwi, Gad le wabwi na Manase le wabwi vaŇčgothiye val…®vaŇčga, na i tabo lenji ghamba yaku.   
\s1 KiŇč…®Ňčgi Josuwa va i kivwalaŇčgi  
\p
\v 7 Josuwa na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® kivwalaŇčgiya kiŇč…®ko wolagh…®ye inanji e ghamba mbaroŇčgi Jor…®dan e yalasiniyeko. Th…® kivwalaŇčgiya kiŇč…®Ňčgiko iri e ghemba idae Balgad, Lebenon e gunuguniye, ghaghad Ou Halak e yaghalako Idom le ghamba mbaro ghadidiye. Josuwa i tagaviyaviya thelauko iyako na i vatomwe weŇčgi ‚ÄĒ vuvura iya uu regha.  
\v 8 Iya thelauko Josuwa va i tagaviyaviya na i vatomweko weŇčgi Isirel, tembe i wova vanautumako bobokuluniye, e bobokuluko r…®gher…®ghenji val…®vaŇčga e yalasiniyeko, Jor…®dan bobokuluniye na bobokulu r…®gher…®ghenji, na val…®vaŇčga e boimako, na vuruvuru vwatavwatae e yaghalako. Iya val…®vaŇčgako thiyako ghar…®ghar…® wabwike thiyake va thiya yakuwe: wabwi Hiti, Amori, Kenani, Perisi, Hivi, na Jebusi.  
\v 9 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® kivwalaŇčgiya kiŇč…®ke e ghembaghembake thiyake:  
\q1 Jeriko gha kiŇč  
\q1 Ai gha kiŇč (ina Betel ghadidiye)  
\v 10   
\q1 Jerusalem gha kiŇč  
\q1 Hebron gha kiŇč  
\v 11   
\q1 Jamut gha kiŇč  
\q1 Lakis gha kiŇč  
\v 12   
\q1 Eglon gha kiŇč  
\q1 Geja gha kiŇč  
\v 13   
\q1 Debi gha kiŇč  
\q1 Geda gha kiŇč  
\v 14   
\q1 Homa gha kiŇč  
\q1 Arad gha kiŇč  
\v 15   
\q1 Lib…®na gha kiŇč  
\q1 Adulam gha kiŇč  
\v 16   
\q1 Makeda gha kiŇč  
\q1 Betel gha kiŇč  
\v 17   
\q1 Tapua gha kiŇč  
\q1 Hepa gha kiŇč  
\v 18   
\q1 Apek gha kiŇč  
\q1 Lasaron gha kiŇč  
\v 19   
\q1 Madon gha kiŇč  
\q1 Hajo gha kiŇč  
\v 20   
\q1 Simiron Meron gha kiŇč  
\q1 Ak…®sap gha kiŇč  
\v 21   
\q1 Tanak gha kiŇč  
\q1 Megido gha kiŇč  
\v 22   
\q1 Kades gha kiŇč  
\q1 Jokneyam ina Kamel gha kiŇč  
\v 23   
\q1 Dor gha kiŇč (ina Napot Dor)  
\q1 Goyim gha kiŇč ina Gilgal  
\v 24   
\q1 Tija gha kiŇč.  
\m Lenji ghanaghanagha theto na regha (31).   
\c 13  
\s1 Val…®vaŇčga tembene th…® wovaŇčgiva  
\p
\v 1 E mbaŇčako iyako Josuwa kaero i amalagh…®sar…® moli. Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero u amalagh…®sar…® moli, ko iyemaeŇčge thelau lagh…®ye mbe inawe ma mba hu wo.   
\p
\v 2 ‚ÄúVal…®vaŇčgake thiyake amba ma hu wo: Pilistiya le ghamba mbaroko lagh…®ye na Gesu le ghamba mbaroŇčgi,  
\v 3 iri e Walagh…®ta Saihor…® Ijipt val…®vaŇčga e boimako, i wa e ghaiwabuko na ve wo Ekron gha teghala, iye Kenan le ghamba mbaro. Pilistiya gha kiŇč…®ke theghelima thiya yaku e ghembaghembake thiyake: Gaja, As…®dod, Eskelon, Gat na Ekron, na vavanava iyaŇčgaiye Avi lenji ghamba mbaro.  
\v 4 Val…®vaŇčga e yaghalako, Kenani lenji val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye, iri Mera, Saidon lenji val…®vaŇčgako ve wo Apek, Amori ghanji teghala.  
\v 5 Gebal lenji val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye; Lebenon lagh…®yeko val…®vaŇčga e boimako, iri Baalgad Ou Hemon raberabe na ve wo Lebo Hamat.   
\p
\v 6 ‚ÄúTembe Ňčgoreiyeva Saidon ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji ghamba mbaroko lagh…®ye, iya thiya yaku e bobokuluko vanautumaniye, Lebenon Ououniye na Misrepot Maim e ghanji lughawoghawo. Ghino ne ya vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake na Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® raka ru e ghamba mbaroko thiyako. U renuwaŇčakiki na u tagaviyaviya thelauke iyake na u giya weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye na lenji ghamba yakuyaku Ňčgora va ya utuma e ghen.  
\v 7 Koino! MbaŇčake u tagaviyaviya thelauke na u giya weŇčgiya uu theghesiwona na Manase gha uu vaŇčgothiye.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Thelau Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro gha tagaviyaviya  
\p
\v 8 Uu Manase vaŇčgothiye, uu Rubin na uu Gad kaerova th…® wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku. Mosese, iye \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo, va i wogiya weŇčgi Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako.   
\p
\v 9 Lenji ghamba yakuyakuko ve wo Aroer…®, Anoni gunuguniye le ghambaghad…® na ghemba ina e gunuguko iyako gha lughawoghawo na malamoko lagh…®ye iri Medeba na ve wo Dibon.  
\v 10 I wa ve wo vara Amon le val…®vaŇčga ghaghadi, na i mban…®vao ghembaghemba KiŇč Saihon va i mbaroŇčaŇčgi, iye Amori lenji kiŇč mbaŇča va i yaku Hesbon e t…®ne na i mbarowe.  
\v 11 Vambe i wova Giliyad, Gesu na Maka lenji val…®vaŇčga. Ou Hemon le val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye na Basan le val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye ghaghadi Saleka.  
\v 12 Na tembe ve wova KiŇč Og le ghamba mbaroko lagh…®ye, iye wabwi Repa moumouniye na va i mbaro Astarot na Edrei e t…®nenji. Mosese va i kivwalaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake na i vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgi.  
\v 13 Ko iyemaeŇčge Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye mava th…® vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiya Gesu na Maka ghar…®ghar…®niye; thiye mbe inanji Isirel e t…®nenji noroke.   
\p
\v 14 Ko iyemaeŇčge Mosese mava i wogiya thelau regha weŇčgiya Livai le wabwi. Ňägoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va le utuutu weya Mosese, thiye lenji yakuyaku kaiwae va i mena weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji vowo mbaŇča th…® bigirawe na th…® Ňčambu na i vorowe Giya Isirel lenji Loi.   
\s1 Mosese va i giya uu na uu lenji ghamba yakuyaku uu Rubin e t…®ne  
\p
\v 15 Mosese va i giya ghamba yakuyakuke iyake weŇčgiya uu na uu, uu Rubin e t…®ne:   
\p
\v 16 Lenji ghamba yakuyakuko va ve wo Aroer…®, Anoni Gunuguniye gha teghala, na ghemba reghava ina e gunuguko gha lughawoghawo, na tembe ve wova malomaloŇčako lagh…®ye i vagh…®liya Medeba.  
\v 17 Hesbon tembe i ruva weiyaŇčgiya ghembaghembako wolagh…®ye e malamoko: Dibon, Bamot Baal, Bet Baalmiyon,  
\v 18 Jahas, Kedemot, Mepat,  
\v 19 Kiriyataim, Sibma, Jeret Saha ina e bobokulu regha, e gunuguko t…®ne,  
\v 20 Bet…®peo, Ou Pisga maloŇčaloŇčaniyeŇčgi, na Bet Jesimot.  
\v 21 I wo ghembaghembako wolagh…®ye e malamoko na Amori lenji kiŇč, Saihon le ghamba mbaroko lagh…®ye, iye va i mbaro Hesbon e t…®ne. Mosese va i kivwala, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Midiya gha rambarombaroke wolagh…®ye thiyeke: Evi, Rekem, Ju, Hu, na Reba. Thiyeke iyake va th…® mbaroŇča val…®vaŇčgako iyako KiŇč Saihon kaiwae.  
\v 22 WeiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake, Balaam Beor nariye iye man…®yeto, Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye vambe th…® un…®gh…®va.  
\v 23 Jor…®dan yalasiniyeko i tabo na uu Rubin lenji ghamba yakuyaku na ghanji teghala. Ghembaghemba nanasiye na lagh…®lagh…®ye va th…® giya weŇčgiya Rubin le wabwi, uu na uu lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Mosese va i giya wabwi na wabwi lenji ghamba yakuyaku uu Gad e t…®ne  
\p
\v 24 Mosese va i giya ghamba yakuyakuke iyake weŇčgiya wabwi na wabwi, uu Gad e t…®ne:   
\p
\v 25 Lenji ghamba yakuyakuko, Jaje na ghembaghembako lagh…®lagh…®ye wolagh…®ye Giliyad e t…®ne, na Amon lenji thelau vaŇčgothiye na ve wo Aroer…®, Raba boimaniyeko.  
\v 26 Lenji ghamba yakuyaku iri Hesbon ve wo Ramat Mij…®pa na Betonim, iri Mahanaim na ve wo Deba gha ghad…®ko.  
\v 27 Jor…®dan Malamoniye e t…®ne i wo Bet Haram, Bet Nimra, Sukot na Japon, KiŇč Saihon le ghamba mbaro va i yaku Hesbon. Walagh…®tae Jor…®dan e yalasiniyeko iye ghanji teghala, na e ghaiwabuko ve wo Njigh…® Galili.  
\v 28 Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye na nanasiyeke thiyake va th…® giya weŇčgiya wabwi na wabwi, uu Gad e t…®ne na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Mosese va i giya uu na uu lenji ghamba yakuyaku wabwi Manase e t…®ne  
\p
\v 29 Mosese va i wogiya thelauko iyako val…®vaŇčga weŇčgiya wabwi na wabwi, uu Manase vaŇčgothiye na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 30 Thelauko iyako iri Mahanaim na i wo e ghaiwabuko. I wo Basan lagh…®yeko na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghembaghemba nanasiye ghembaewona, iyava mbaŇča regha Jai i kivwalaŇčgi na i wo val…®vaŇčgako iyako. Va mbaŇča regha KiŇč Og, Basan e t…®ne i mbaroŇča iya val…®vaŇčgako iyako.  
\v 31 Va i wo Giliyad vaŇčgothiye regha na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Astarot na Edrei. Ghembaghembake thiyake KiŇč Og va i yaku Basan le ghamba mbaroko ghembaghembaniye lagh…®lagh…®ye. Iya val…®vaŇčgako iyako va i wogiya weya uu Maki, iye Manase nariye.   
\p
\v 32 Mosese va i giya thelauko iyako Ňčgoreiye varako Jeriko na Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro mbaŇča va ina Mowab e malamoniye.  
\v 33 Ko iyemaeŇčge Mosese mava i wogiya mun thelau regha weŇčgiya Livai le wabwi. Va iŇča, lenji yakuyaku kaiwae ne i mena weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye mbaŇča ne th…® vakatha vowo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.   
\c 14  
\s1 Josuwa i tagaviyaviya thelauko lagh…®ye e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i njanja i wogiya weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye  
\p
\v 1 Iyake i govambwara va ŇčgoroŇčga na th…® giya Kenan thelauniyeko ‚ÄĒ Jor…®dan yalasiniyeko th…® wogiya weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye. Eliyesa iye ravowovowo, Josuwa Nan nariye na Isirel uu theyaworo na theghewo lenji randevivaŇčgi, th…® giya thelauko weŇčgi Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.  
\v 2 MbaŇča va th…® giya ghamba yakuyaku weŇčgi wabwi na wabwi, uu theghesiwo na uu Manase vaŇčgothiye weŇčgi, va th…® duda var…® na var…®ko le govambwara th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye, Ňčgora \nd Giya Loi\nd* vama i utu giyawe Mosese.  
\v 3-4 Mosese kaerova i giya ghamba yakuyaku weŇčgi uu theghewo na uu reghava vaŇčgothiye, Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako. (Josep orumburumbuye va uu theghewo: Manase na Ip…®reim.) IyemaeŇčge, Mosese mava i wogiya ghamba yakuyaku regha weŇčgi uu Livai e val…®vaŇčgako iyako. Ko vambe i vatomwe eŇčge thiya yaku e ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye na umauma inanjiwe lenji thetheghan…®ko lenji ghamba ghan nana.  
\v 5 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® giya lenji thelauko e val…®vaŇčgako iyako Ňčgoreiye vara iyako, Ňčgora \nd Giya Loi\nd* vama i utu giya weya Mosese.   
\s1 Josuwa i wogiya ghemba Hebron weya Keleb  
\p
\v 6 MbaŇča regha ghar…®ghar…® vavana Juda e gha uu t…®ne th…® raka menawe Josuwa mbaŇča vamba inanji Gilgal e t…®ne. Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake regha, Keleb Jepune nariye na i mena uu Keni e t…®ne, i dagewe Josuwa iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero u ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i dagewe Mosese, Loi le lolo, ghen na ghino kaiwanda mbaŇča va inanda Kades Beniya e t…®ne.  
\v 7 Ghino wo theghathegha vama i wo ghwevar…® mbaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo, Mosese va i variyeŇčgo Kades Beniya e t…®ne ya raŇčgi na ya mena ya ghewaŇča budakai ina e thelauke iyake t…®ne. MbaŇča ya njoghawe, ya wonjogha toto emunjoruwe amalagh…®niye budakai va ya thuwe e maraŇčgu.  
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge wouneko va weiŇčguyaŇčgiko th…® vakatha gharelagh…®lagh…® lagh…®ye weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye. IyemaeŇčge, ghino ya vareminje moli Giya lo Loi.  
\v 9 Iya kaiwae Mosese i tholo na i dagera e ghino, iŇča, ‚ÄėIya vara thelauna mendava vo loŇčganawe nevole ghen na orumburumbu tha na tha lenji ghamba yakuyaku mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye, kaiwae mendava u ghambu na u vareminja Giya lo Loi e gharen…®na lagh…®ye.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 10 ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, noroke kaero theghathegha kaero ghwevar…® na umbolima iko mbaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i utu giya utuutuko iyako weya Mosese. Va e mbaŇčako iyako Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye vamba th…® rakaraka loloŇčga e vuruvuru vwatavwatae, na \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Ňčgoreiye va le dagerawe, i vakathaŇčgo mbe e yawayawaliŇčgu ghaghad…® noroke. Wo u thuweŇčgo noroke! Wo theghathegha kaero i wo ghwewa na umbolima (85)  
\v 11 na lo vur…®gheghe noroke mbe Ňčgora vara Mosese vamba e yawayawaliye na i variyeŇčgo ya mena gheke. Lo vur…®ghegheke mbe val…®kaiwaŇčgu eŇčge ya wa gaith…® kaiwae o ya vakathava the bigithan.  
\v 12 Iya kaiwae noroke mau vatomwe eŇčge weŇčgo vanautumake e ououniyeke iya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i dagerake weŇčgo va e mbaŇčako iyako. Kaerova wo utu giya e ghen ghar…®ghar…® lagh…®lagh…®ye idanji Anak inanji gheko, na ghembaghembako ghanji gana mbe th…® vur…®gheghe eŇčge. Ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i thalavuŇčgo na ya vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgi Ňčgoreiya va iŇčako.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 13 Josuwa i wogiyawe Keleb, Jepune nariye gha dagemwaewo na i wogiya ghambae idae Hebron na le ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 14 Hebron mbe Keleb, Jepune rara Keni nariye orumburumbuye lenji ghamba yakuyaku vara, kaiwae va i vareminje na i ghambu \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Isirel lenji Loi.  
\v 15 Hebron vambe idae Kiriyat Aba, iye va lolo lagh…®ye regha wabwi Anak e t…®ne.   
\c 15  
\s1 Thelauko iya Juda le wabwiko va th…® wo  
\p
\v 1 Thelauko iya wabwi na wabwi va th…® wo Juda le uu e t…®ne le lagh…®lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiyake:  
\p Thelauko iyako i wo ghaghad Idom le ghamba mbaroko na ve wo vuruvuru vwatavwata idae Jin e yaghalako.  
\v 2 Iya teghalako val…®vaŇčga e yaghalako ve wo Njigh…® Maremareniye ghaghadiko.  
\v 3 I reŇča e yaghalaniyeko, iri Akrabim GhambareŇča na ve wo Jin. I ruku reŇča Kades Beniya e yaghalaniyeko, i ghathara Hesron i voro Ada, i loŇčga na i ghembaya Kaka.  
\v 4 I loŇčga na i ghembeya Asimon na i mbele mbwa regha Ňčgora Ijipt ghaghad…®ko, na ve wo Njigh…® Meditareiniyan. Iyake vanautumako ghaghad vara iyako, val…®vaŇčga e yaghalako.   
\p
\v 5 Njigh…® Maremareniye e boimako iye teghala, i voro ve wo Jor…®dan na i mena i wo Ňčgora i varaŇčgikowe.  
\p Ghaiwabuko gha teghala i ri gheko  
\v 6 i wa ve wo Bet Hog…®la, i reŇča Jor…®dan Malamoniye e ghaiwabuniyeko, na i voro ve wo Var…® Bohan (Bohan iye Rubin va nariye).  
\v 7 Teghalako i ri Ako Malamoniye i voro Debi, na i loŇčga na i ghembeya ghaiwabuko, Gilgal gha ghaoko, amba i ghembeya Adumim GhambareŇča, val…®vaŇčga e yaghalaniyeko. Amba i wa ve wo En Semes mbwaniyeŇčgi na ve raŇčgi En Rogel.  
\v 8 Amba i mbeleya Hinom Malamoniye, i reŇča e bobokulu regha e yaghalaniyeko Ňčgora Jebusi va th…® vatada ghambanji lagh…®yewe ‚ÄĒ Jerusalem. Teghalako i voro e bobokulu regha vwatae, Hinom Malamoniye e t…®ne val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko, na Repa Malamoniye gha teghala, e ghaiwabuko.  
\v 9 Amba teghalako e ouko vwatae i loŇčga na i ghemba Mbwa Nep…®towa na ve raŇčgi e ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye Ou Epron ghadidiye. Gheko amba i loŇčga na i ghemba Baala (o Kiriyat Jeyarim).  
\v 10 Teghalako i vagh…®liya Bala e yalasiniyeko na ve wo Ou Seir, i ghathara Ou Jeyarim (Kesalon), i ghembeghembeya ghaiwabuko na i njaoko Bet Semes na i roiteta Tim…®na.  
\v 11 Teghalako i wa ve reŇča Ekron bobokuluniye e ghaiwabuko. I loŇčga na i ghembeya Sikeron, i iteta Ou Bala na ve wo Jab…®nil. Teghalako ve raŇčgi vara e Njigh…® Meditareiniyan.  
\v 12 Teghala e yalasiko, iye Njigh…® Meditareiniyan weiye njigh…®ko ghadidiye.  
\p Iya vara teghalaŇčgike thiyake e t…®nenji, Juda gha uu ghar…®ghar…®niye thiya yakuwe.   
\s1 Keleb i kivwalaŇčgiya ghembaghemba ghembaiwoke thiyake ‚ÄĒ Hebron na Debi  
\p
\v 13 Ňägoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i utu giya weya Josuwa, iya val…®vaŇčgako va i wogiya weya Juda, ghadidiye regha i vatomwe weya Keleb Jepune nariye, i mena uu Juda e t…®ne. Keleb va i wo ghemba idae Hebron. Ghembake iyake Aba, Anak ramae ghambae.  
\v 14 Keleb i vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiya Anak orumburumbuye e ghembako t…®ne ‚ÄĒ wabwi Sesai, Ahiman, na Tal…®mai.  
\v 15 Amba i wareri gheko na ve gaith…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® thiya yaku Debi e t…®ne (ghembake iyake vambe idae Kiriyat Sepa).  
\v 16 Keleb iŇča, ‚ÄúThela thoŇčgo i kivwalaŇčgiya Kiriyat Sepa na i wo ghembako ne ya vaŇčgu giya yawarumbuŇčguke, Ak…®sa, weya amalagh…®niye na i vaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ  
\v 17 Ot…®niyel, iye Keleb ghaghae Kenas nariye, va i kivwalaŇčgiya ghembako iyako, iya kaiwae Keleb i vaŇčgu giya yawarumbuye Ak…®sa weya amalagh…®niye na i vaŇčgu.   
\p
\v 18 MbaŇča ghe gha mbaŇča Ak…®sa i mena weya Ot…®niyel, amba Ot…®niyel i dagewe na i naŇčgoya thelau, ghamba kaiwo weya ramae. MbaŇča Ak…®sa i nja ele doŇč…®kiko, Keleb i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vakatha budakai kaiwan?‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 19 I gonjoghawe, iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero mendava u wogiya thelau e ghino ina e val…®vaŇčga ma mbwa inawe. Iya kaiwae nuwaŇčguiya mbwarowou vavana.‚ÄĚ Kaero Keleb i giyawe mbwarowou theghewo ‚ÄĒ regha yavoro na regha bode.   
\s1 Juda ghembaghembaniye lagh…®lagh…®ye  
\p
\v 20 Iya thelauke iyake Juda le wabwi, uu na uu va th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 21 Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye th…® rotan e yaghalako thiye kaiwanji, va inanji Ňčgora Idom gha teghalako, thiye iyake: Kab…®jil, Eda, Jagu,  
\v 22 Kina, Dimona, Adada,  
\v 23 Kades, Hajo, It…®nan,  
\v 24 Jip, Telem, Beyalot,  
\v 25 Hajo Hadata, Kiriyot Hesron (o Hajo)  
\v 26 Amam, Sema, Molada,  
\v 27 Haja Gada, Hesmon, Bet…®pelet,  
\v 28 Haja Sual, Beyasiba, Bijiyotiya,  
\v 29 Baala, Iyim, Ejem,  
\v 30 El…®tolad, Kesil, Homa,  
\v 31 Jik…®lag, Mad…®mana, San…®sana,  
\v 32 Lebaot, Silhim, Ain, na Rimon. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghanaghanagha vara ghembayeiwo na ghambasiwo weinjiyaŇčjiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 33 Ghembaghemba inanji e ououko r…®gher…®ghenji thiyake:  
\p Estaol, Jora, As…®na,  
\v 34 Janoa, En Ganim, Tapua, Enam,  
\v 35 Jamut, Adulam, Soko, Ajeka,  
\v 36 Saaraim, Aditaim, Gedera na Gaderotaim. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghanaghanagha vara ghembayaworo na ghembavar…® weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 37 ghembaghembake thiyake vambe inanjiva gheko: Jenan, Hadasa, Mig…®dal Gad,  
\v 38 Dileyan, Mij…®pa, Jok…®til,  
\v 39 Lakis, Boj…®kat, Eglon,  
\v 40 Kabon, Lamas, Kit…®lis,  
\v 41 Gederot, Bet…®dagon, Naama, na Makeda. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghanaghanagha vara ghembayaworo na ghembawona weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 42 Ghembaghembake thiyake vambe inanji weva:  
\p Lib…®na, Eta, Asan,  
\v 43 Ip…®ta, As…®na, Nejib,  
\v 44 Keila, Ak…®jib, na Maresa. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghanaghanagha vara ghembasiwo weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 45 Ghembaghembake thiyake vambe inanji weva: Ghemba lagh…®ye Ekron weiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye,  
\v 46 na ghembaghembako lagh…®lagh…®ye na nanasiye wolagh…®ye As…®dod ghadidiye, i ri Ekron na ve wo Njigh…® Meditareiniyan.   
\p
\v 47 Ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye thiyake vambe inanji weva: As…®dod na Gaja, weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye ve wo Ijipt gha teghalako, e mbwa regha na Njigh…® Meditareiniyan ghadidiye.   
\p
\v 48 E bobokuluko vanautumaniye vambe iyava ghembaghembake thiyake inanjiwe:  
\p Sami, Jati, Soko,  
\v 49 Dana, Kiriyat Sepa, (o Debi),  
\v 50 Anab, Es…®temo, Anim,  
\v 51 Gosen, Holon, na Gilo. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembayaworo na ghembara, weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 52 Ghembaghembake thiyake vambe inanjiva gheko: Arab, Duma, Esan,  
\v 53 Janim, Bet Tapua, Apeka,  
\v 54 Humta, Hebron, na Jiyo: ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembasiwo, weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 55 Ghembaghembake thiyake vambe inanjiva gheko: Mayon, Kamel, Jip, Juta,  
\v 56 Jes…®ril, Jok…®dim, Janoa,  
\v 57 Kein, Gibeya na Tim…®na. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghanaghanagha vara ghembayaworo, weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 58 Ghembaghembake thiyake vambe inanjiva gheko: Halhul, Bet…®ju, Gedo,  
\v 59 Marat, Betanot, na Eltekon. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye lenji ghanaghanagha ghembawona, weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 60 Ghembaghembake thiyake vambe inanjiva gheko: Kiriyat Baal (o Kiriyat Jeyarim), na Raba. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembaiwo weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 61 E vuruvuru vwatavwatae ghembaghembake thiyake va inanjiwe: Bet Araba, Midin, Sekaka,  
\v 62 Nib…®san, Njigh…® Ghembaniye na En Gedi. Ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye thiyake, lenji ghanaghanagha vara ghembawona, weinjiyaŇčgiya ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanjiva.   
\p
\v 63 Ko iyemaeŇčge Juda gha uu ghar…®ghar…®niye mava val…®kaiwanji th…® vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiya Jebusi ghar…®ghar…®niye. Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake va thiya yaku Jerusalem t…®ne. Jebusi vambe inanji gheko thiya yaku weinjiyaŇčgiya Juda gha uu ghar…®ghar…®niye.   
\c 16  
\s1 Uu Ip…®reim na uu Manase vaŇčgothiye lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 1 Thelauko ghaghad iya Josep orumburumbuyeko va th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku e yaghalako, iri Jeriko mbwarowouniyeŇčgi val…®vaŇčga e boimako, e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan ghadidiye. Amba i iteta Jeriko i loŇčga na i ghembeya ghaiwabuko e vuruvuru vwatavwata, i ghathara e bobokulu vanautumaniye na ve wo Betel.  
\v 2 Iri Betel i wa Luji, i wa Atarot Ada, iya Ar…®k ghar…®ghar…®niye thiya yakuwe.  
\v 3 Kaero i loŇčga na i ghembeya yalasiko na ve wo Jep…®let ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji ghamba yaku, tembema ve wo eŇčge Bet Horon Bode na i wa Geja na ghaghad…® Njigh…® Meditareiniyan.   
\p
\v 4 Josep orumburumbuye, uu Ip…®reim na uu Manase vaŇčgothiye va th…® wo thelauke iyake na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Uu Ip…®reim lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 5 Iyake uu Ip…®reim, wabwi na wabwi lenji ghamba yakuyaku:  
\p Ghanji teghala iri Atarot Ada i loŇčga na i ghembeya boimako, i wa ve wo Bet Horon Yavoro,  
\v 6 na gheko ve wo Njigh…® Meditareiniyan. Mik…®metat va ina e ghaiwabuko. Iri gheko na val…®vaŇčga e boimako, teghalako i mwavathawo na i ghembeya Taanat Sailo. Na iteteŇča iyako na i loŇčga ghembeya boimako na ve wo Janoa.  
\v 7 Amba iri Janoa na i loŇčga na i nja i wa Atarot na Nara, ve wo Jeriko, ghaghad Jor…®dan.  
\v 8 Teghalako i loŇčga na i njaoko iri Tapua, ve wo mbwarowou Kana na ghaghad Njigh…® Meditareiniyan. Iya thelauke iyake va i wogiya weŇčgiya wabwi na wabwi, Ip…®reim gha uu e t…®ne na lenji ghamba yakuyaku,  
\v 9 weiye ghembaghemba nanasiye vavanava, iyava inanji uu Manase e lenji ghamba yakuyaku t…®ne, ko iyemaeŇčge vama i wogiya weŇčgiya uu Ip…®reim.  
\v 10 Ko iyemaeŇčge mava th…® vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgi Kenan ghar…®ghar…®niye iya va thiya yakuko Geja. Vambe thiya yaku vara weinjiyaŇčgi ghaghad mbaŇčake iyake, ko iyemaeŇčge th…® vavothaŇčaŇčgi na th…® tabo lenji rakakaiwobwagaŇčgi.   
\c 17  
\p
\v 1 Thelauko regha iya Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko va i giya weŇčgiya tari vavana, th…® raka mena Manase gha uu e t…®ne. Manase iye Josep nariye lagh…®yeniye. Maki iye Giliyad ramae, Manase le ŇčgamaŇčgama lagh…®yeninji na iye ragagaith…® thovuye regha, iya kaiwae Giliyad na Basan, Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako va i wo na le ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 2 Thelau ina Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko va i giya weŇčgiya wabwi na wabwi, Manase e gha uu t…®ne, iyava vavanake thiyake; Abiyesa, Helek, Asriyel, Sekem, Hepa, na Semida. Thiyake gh…®mogh…®moru th…® raka mena Manase e gha uu t…®ne, iye Josep nariye na thiye tari regha na regha umbal…®nji.   
\p
\v 3 Jelopehad, Hepe nariye, na Hepe iye Giliyad nariye, na Giliyad iye Mekiri nariye, na Mekiri iye Manase nariye. Jelopehad mava ele ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru, ko iyemaeŇčge vambe i ghamb…®Ňčgi eŇčge wanakau theulima. Idaidanji thiyake: Mala, Nowa, Hog…®la, Milika, na Tija.  
\v 4 Wanakauke thiyake th…® raka weya Eliyesa, iye ravowovowo, Josuwa Nan nariye na randevivaŇčgi, na th…®Ňča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* kaerova i dage weya Mosese ne hu wogiya weime, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva lama bodabodako gh…®mogh…®moruko, thelauke iyake regha lama ghamba yakuyaku.‚ÄĚ Kaero Ňčgoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i uturawe, th…® wogiya thelau regha weŇčgi, Ňčgoreiya va th…® giya weŇčgiya lenji bodaboda gh…®mogh…®moruko.  
\v 5-6 Iyako kaiwae Josuwa i giya Manase orumburumbuye gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau thelau vuvuyaworo Walagh…®tae Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko na ghamba mbaro theghewo; Giliyad na Basan val…®vaŇčga e boimako.   
\p
\v 7 Uu Manase lenji ghamba yakuyaku iri Asa ele val…®vaŇčga ve wo Mik…®metat, Sekem val…®vaŇčga e boimako. Teghalako i wa e yaghalako na ve wo En-Tapua Ňčgora ghar…®ghar…® thiya yakuwe.  
\v 8 Thelauko iya i vagh…®liya Tapua, mbe Manase le thelau, ko iyemaeŇčge ghembako Tapua, iya e teghalako t…®ne, Epreim orumburumbuye weŇčgi.  
\v 9-10 Gad, e yaghalako i mbeleya mbwa regha ‚ÄĒ Kana i voru na i njaoko na ve varaŇčgi Meditareiniyan. Manase le val…®vaŇčga ina e mbwa Kana val…®vaŇčga ghaiwabuko, ko iyemaeŇčge e yaghalako ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye vavana inanjiwe, uu Ip…®reim weŇčgi, othembe va ina Manase ele val…®vaŇčga t…®ne. E ghaiwabuko Manase weiye uu Asa ghanjighad regha, na e ghaiwabuko na boimako Manase gha teghalako regha weiye wabwi Isaka.   
\p
\v 11 Isaka na Asa e lenji val…®vaŇčgako t…®ne ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye vavana nanjiwe, uu Manase weŇčgi. Ghembaghembake thiyake: Bet San na Ib…®liyam, na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanjiva, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Dor (ina e njigh…®ko ghadidiye), Endo, Tanak, Megido, na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanji.  
\v 12 IyemaeŇčge Manase gha uu ghar…®ghar…®niye ma va val…®kaiwanji thiya yaku e ghembaghembako thiyako t…®nenji, kaiwae Kenani ghar…®ghar…®niye vambe th…® rovur…®ghegheŇča vara thiya yaku weŇčgi.  
\v 13 Othembe Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye vama th…® mbuthu na th…® vur…®gheghe mava th…® vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgi, vama th…® vakathaŇčgi eŇčge rakakaiwobwaga weŇčgi.   
\p
\v 14 Josep orumburumbuye th…® dage weya Josuwa, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mbe u wogiya eŇčge weime thelau vuvura na lama ghamba yakuyaku? Lama wabwike i lagh…®ye moli kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* i mwaewo weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 15 Josuwa i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo lemi wabwi kaero i lagh…®ye moli na bobokuluna vanautumaniye, iya uu Ip…®reim lenji ghamba yakuyakuna i nasiye moli, ko hu raka e njamnjam…®ko na vohu guriya thelau kaiwami, iya Perisi na Repa lenji ghamba yakuyakuko e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Josep orumburumbuye th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúVanautumako e ououniyeko ma val…®kaiwame, na Kenani ghar…®ghar…®niye iya thiya yaku e malamoŇčgiko lenji waŇčga momod…® th…® vakathaŇčgi e aiyan. Iya thiya yakuko Bet San na ghembaghemba evasiwanjiva na thavala thiya yaku Jes…®ril e Malamoniye.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 17 Josuwa i dage weŇčgiya uu Ip…®reim na uu Manase val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko, iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero wabwi lagh…®ye moliya ghemi na hu vur…®gheghe moli. Ne hu wo lemi thelau ma e vwataeva.  
\v 18 Vanautumako e ououniyeko ne hu wo, othembe iye njamnjam…®bwaga. Ne hu guri, hu iku na hu wo lemi ghamba yakuyaku e val…®vaŇčga regha na ve wo val…®vaŇčga regha. Iya Kenani ghar…®ghar…®niyeko ne hu vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgi, othembe lenji waŇčga momod…®Ňčgi Ňčginaunjiya aiyan na thiye tembe ghar…®ghar…® vur…®ghegheŇčgiva.‚ÄĚ   
\c 18  
\s1 Josuwa i giyavuna thelauko wabwiko vavana weŇčgi  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča kaero th…® kivalaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e thelauko iyako t…®ne na e ghereiye, amba Isirel wabwiko lagh…®ye th…® mevathavatha Sailo e t…®ne na th…® vatada Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye gheko.  
\v 2 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye uu theghepir…® vamba inanjiwe, ma vamba e lenji ghamba yakuyaku e thelauko iyako t…®ne.   
\p
\v 3 Josuwa i vaitoŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye, iŇča, ‚ÄúNe hu roroghagha mbaŇča le molomolao ŇčgoroŇčga, amba muyai hu raka ru na hu wo thelauko iya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, orumburumbumi lenji Loi, vama i wogiyako e ghemi?  
\v 4 Hu tuthiŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru thegheto wabwi regha iya e t…®ne. Ne ya variyeŇčgi th…® raka na veth…® r…®gh…®ya thelauko na th…® ten…®Ňčgi e wabwi regha iya. Amba th…® raka njoghama e ghino.  
\v 5 Ne hu tena thelauko na vuvupir…®. Juda mbe i yaku ele val…®vaŇčgako e ghaiwabuko.  
\v 6 Hu rori njoŇča lemi vavanamwe thelau utuutuniye na hu limena e ghino. Amba ne ya du var…®var…®ke var…®iwoke kaiwami Giya la Loi e marae.  
\v 7 IyemaeŇčge uu Livai mane th…® wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku regha e t…®nemina, lenji yakuyaku kaiwae, thiye ne th…® tabo ravowovowo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva wabwike thiyake: Gad, Rubin na Manase vaŇčgothiye kaerova th…® wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako. Mosese \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo vama i wogiya weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 8 Kaero gh…®mogh…®moruma th…® raka na veth…® r…®gh…®ya thelauko mbaŇča Josuwa i utuvao utuutuke iyake weŇčgi: ‚ÄúHu raka na vohu r…®gh…®ya thelauna na hu rori njoŇča utuutuniye. Amba hu raka njoghama e ghino, na ya du var…®var…®ke var…®iwoke \nd Giya Loi\nd* e marae kaiwami gheke ‚ÄĒ Sailo e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 Kaero gh…®mogh…®moruma th…® raka na veth…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya me utugiyama weŇčgi. Th…® rori njogha utuutuniyeko ŇčgoroŇčga meth…® giya na th…®Ňča e uu theghepir…®ko na tembe Ňčgorava ghembaghemba regha na regha. Amba th…® raka njogha weya Josuwa e lenji kiyamu Sailo e t…®ne.  
\v 10 Amba Josuwa i du var…®var…® var…®iwo \nd Giya Loi\nd* e marae kaiwanji Sailo e t…®ne, na i govambwara thelauko gha tagaviyaviya weŇčgiya Isirel, uu na uu iya ma mba e lenji ghamba yakuyakuko.   
\s1 Wabwi Benjamin lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 11 Var…®var…®ma var…®iwoma th…® woraŇčgiyakai vara wabwi Benjamin, uu na uu. Lenji ghamba yakuyaku Josuwa i wogiya weŇčgi va ina uu Juda na uu Josep ghanjilughawoghawo.   
\p
\v 12 E ghaiwabuko ghanji teghala iri Jor…®dan, i voroŇča malomaloŇča Jeriko e ghaiwabuniyeko, i loŇčga na i wa e yalasiko, i ghathara e bobokulu vanautumaniye, na ve raŇčgi e vuruvuru vwatavwatae Bet Aven e t…®ne.  
\v 13 Iri gheko i lawa ve wo malomaloŇča, Luji (idae regha Betel) e yaghalako na i wa ve nja Atarot Ada, i voroŇča ou regha e yaghalako, Bet Horon Bode/Raberabe.   
\p
\v 14 E bobokuluko i loŇčga na i ghembeya Bet Horon e yaghalako, teghalako i wa e yaghalako val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko na ve raŇčgi Kiriyat Baal (o Kiriyat Jeyarim), ghembake iyake Juda gha uu ghambanji. Iyako ghanji teghala val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko.   
\p
\v 15 Teghala val…®vaŇčga e yaghalako iri Kiriyat Jeyarim ina e yalasiko na ve raŇčgi e mbwarowou Nep…®towa.  
\v 16 I wa ve nja e ouko r…®ghe na ghamwa i nja e Malamo Hinom, Malamo Repa ghaiwabuniyeko. I loŇčga na ghemba yaghalako i ghathara Hinom Malamoniye, Jebusi ghadidiye e yaghalaniyeko na i ghembeya En Rogel.  
\v 17 Teghalako i mwanavathawo, i loŇčga na i ghemba ghaiwabuko ve wo En Semes na mbowa i wava ve wo Gelilot Adumim Pas/GhambareŇča val…®vaŇčgava. Teghalako i loŇčga i nja ve wo Var…® Bohan ‚ÄĒ Bohan iye va Rubin nariye.  
\v 18 Iri gheko, teghalako i loŇčga na i ghembeya ghemba Bet Araba ghaiwabuko ghaghad…® na i nja Walagh…®tae Jor…®dan gunuguniye.  
\v 19 Amba i loŇčga na i ghembeya Bet Hog…®la gharere vwatae val…®vaŇčga ghaiwabuko na ve raŇčgi e garoworu regha Njigh…® Maremareniye e ghaiwabuko, Jor…®dan ve varaŇčgikowe e yaghalako. I yake teghala e yaghalako.   
\p
\v 20 Jor…®dan i tabo na teghala val…®vaŇčga e boimako. Thiyake Benjamin gha wabwi, uu na uu va th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku ghanjighad…®Ňčgi.   
\p
\v 21 Wabwi Benjamin, uu na uu va th…® mbana ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye thiyake:  
\p Jeriko, Bet Hog…®la, Emek Keji,  
\v 22 Bet Araba, Jemaraim, Betel,  
\v 23 Avi, Para, Op…®ra,  
\v 24 Kepara Amon, Op…®ni na Geba. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghambayaworo na ghembaiwo na ghembaghemba nanasiyeva evasiwanji.   
\p
\v 25 Ghembaghembake thiyake tembe Ňčgoreiyeva: Gibiyon, Rama, Berot,  
\v 26 Mij…®pa, Kepira, Moja,  
\v 27 Rekem, Ipel, Tarala,  
\v 28 Jela, Haelep, Jebu (o Jerusalem), Gibeya na Kiriyat Jeyarim. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembayaworo na ghembavar…® na ghembaghemba nanasiye vavanava evasiwanji. Thelauke iyake uu na uu Benjamin e gha wabwi t…®ne va th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\c 19  
\s1 Simiyon le ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 1 Var…®var…®ma var…®iwoma th…® govambwara wabwi theghewoniye iye Simiyon gha wabwi, uu na uu th…® mena na th…® wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku. Lenji ghamba yakuyakuko va ina wabwi Juda lenji thelau e t…®ne.  
\v 2 Ghembaghembake thiyake va inanji e t…®ne:  
\p Beyasiba, Molada,  
\v 3 Haja Sual, Baala, Ejem,  
\v 4 El…®tolad, Betul, Homa,  
\v 5 Jik…®lag, Bet Makabot, Haja Susa,  
\v 6 Bet Lebaot na Saruhen. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembayaworo na ghembato na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanjiva.   
\p
\v 7 Ghembaghembake thiyake tembe Ňčgoreiyeva: Ain, Rimon, Eta, na Asan. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembavar…® na nanasiye tembe evasiwanjiva.  
\v 8 Ghembaghembako lagh…®lagh…®ye na nanasiye evasiwanjiko i wa ve wo Baalat Beya (o Rama), ina val…®vaŇčga e yaghalako. Thelauke iyake uu na uu Simiyon e gha wabwi t…®ne th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 9 Kaiwae wabwi Juda lenji ghamba yakuyaku va i lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgi, iya kaiwae va th…® wogiya val…®vaŇčga regha weŇčgiya Simiyon gha wabwi.   
\s1 Sebulon (Jebulon) gha tari lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 10 Var…®var…®ma var…®iwoma th…® woraŇčgiya Sebulon gha wabwi, uu na uu th…® wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku. Ghamba yakuyakuko iyako va i wa ve wo Sarid.  
\v 11 Gheko teghalako i loŇčga na i ghembeya yalasiko na ve wo Marala, ve laweya Dabeset na mbwa Jok…®neyam val…®vaŇčga e boimako.  
\v 12 Sarid val…®vaŇčga regha teghalako i loŇčga na i wa e boimako na ve wo Kis…®lot Tabor ghaghad, amba i wa Daberat na i voro Japiya.  
\v 13 Mbowo i ghaova e boimako na gheko ve wo Gat Hepa na Et Kajin, i mwanavathawo na i ghembeya Neya gha ghawoko i loŇčga na i ghembeya Rimon.  
\v 14 E ghaiwabuko, teghalako i loŇčga na i ghembeya Hanaton, na ve ghad Ip…®ta El malamoniye.  
\v 15 Na ghembaghembake thiyake tembe inanjiweva: Katat, Nahalal, Simiron, Aidala, na Bet…®lehem: ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembayaworo na ghembaiwo na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanjiva.  
\v 16 Ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye thiyake na ghembaghemba nanasiye e thelauke iyake t…®ne, uu na uu Sebulon e gha wabwi t…®ne th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Isaka gha tari lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 17 Var…®var…®ma var…®iwoma th…® woraŇčgiya wabwi Isaka, uu na uu th…® tabo wabwivar…®nji th…® wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 18 Ghamba yakuyakuko iyako i wo Jej…®ril, Kesulot, Sunem,  
\v 19 Haparaim, Siyon, Anaharat,  
\v 20 Rabit, Kisiyon, Ebes,  
\v 21 Remet, En Ganim, En-Hada, Bet…®pajej…®,  
\v 22 teghalako tembe ve wova Tabo, Sahajuma na Bet Semes, na Jor…®dan iye teghala. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembayaworo na ghembawona weiye ghembaghemba nanasiyeva evasiwanji.  
\v 23 Iyake Isaka gha wabwi, uu na uu lenji ghamba yakuyaku, iya ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye na ghembaghemba nanasiye thiyake.   
\s1 Asa gha uu lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 24 Var…®var…®ma var…®iwoma th…® woraŇčgiya Asa gha wabwi, uu na uu th…® tabo wabwilimaninji th…® wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 25 Lenji ghamba yakuyakuko va i mban…®Ňčgiya:  
\p Hel…®kat, Hali, Beten, Ak…®sap,  
\v 26 Alam Melek, Amad, na Misal. Teghala val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko i mban…®Ňčgiya Kamel, na Siho Lib…®nat.  
\v 27 Amba i mwanavathawo na i loŇčga na i vorowoko e boimako, ghamwae i ghembeya Bet Dagon, ve wo Sebulon na Ip…®ta El Malamoniye, na iwa e ghaiwabuko ve wo Bet Emek na Neiyel. Mbowo i loŇčga na i ghembeva ghaiwabuko ve wo Kabul,  
\v 28 Ebron Rehob, Hamon, na Kana ghaghad Saidon.  
\v 29 Ghamba ghad…®ko ve njogha na ghamwae i ghembeya Rama na ve wova Taiya ‚ÄĒ ghemba gha gana vur…®vur…®ghegheniye. Amba i loŇčga na i ghembeya Hosa, e yalasiko na ve ghad Njigh…® Meditareiniyan. Tembe i wova Ak…®jib,  
\v 30 Uma, Apek, na Rehob. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembayeiwo na ghembaiwo na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanjiva.  
\v 31 Ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye na nanasiye thiyake inanji e thelauko iya uu na uu, Asa e gha wabwi t…®ne th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Nap…®talai le wabwi lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 32 Var…®var…®ma var…®iwoma th…® woraŇčgiya Nap…®talai gha wabwi, uu na uu th…® tabo wabwiwonaninji th…® wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 33 Teghalako va iri Helep ve wo umbwa lagh…®ye ouk ina e ou regha, Jaananim e t…®ne, i wa Adami-Nekeb na ve wo Jab…®nil, ve lawa Lakam na gha teghala Jor…®dan.  
\v 34 Gheko, teghalako i loŇčga na i njaoko e yalasiko i wa Aj…®not Tabo, amba i wa Hukok, ve wo Sebulon e yaghalako, Asa e yalasiko na Jor…®dan e boimako.  
\v 35 Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye e ghanjigana thiyake: Jidim, Je, Hamat, Rakat, Kiniret,  
\v 36 Adama, Rama, Hajo,  
\v 37 Kades, Edrei, En Hajo,  
\v 38 Yiron, Mig…®dal El, Horem, Betanat na Bet Semes. Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye ghembayaworo na ghembasiwo na ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwanjiva.  
\v 39 Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye na nanasiye thiyake va inanji e thelauke iyake t…®ne uu na uu, Nap…®talai gha wabwi th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Den gha uu lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 40 Var…®var…®ma var…®iwoma th…® woraŇčgiya Den gha wabwi, uu na uu th…® tabo wabwipir…®ninji th…® wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 41 Ghamba yakuyakuko iyako va i wo Jora, Estaol, Ir Semes,  
\v 42 Salbim, Aijalon, It…®la,  
\v 43 Elon, Tim…®na, Ekron,  
\v 44 El…®teke, Gibeton, Baalat,  
\v 45 Jehud, Beneberak, Gat-Rimon,  
\v 46 Me Jakon na Rakon tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghambambaro, Jopa ele val…®vaŇčga.   
\p
\v 47 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča Den le wabwi ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® th…®vaiya lenji ghamba yakuyakuko, th…® raka na veth…® gaith…® Les na th…® kivwalaŇčgi. Th…® gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko na th…® wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku. Thiya yaku gheko na th…® wogiya ghembako idae togha Den, rumbunji Den le ghaida.  
\v 48 Ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye na nanasiye thiyake uu na uu, Den e gha wabwi t…®ne th…® wo na lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Josuwa le ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 49 MbaŇča Isirel lenji randevivaŇčgiko kaero th…® giyavao thelauko iyako weŇčgiya uu na uu, wabwi Isirel e t…®nenji, amba th…® wogiyava Josuwa Nan nariye le ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 50 Ňägoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i utu giya weŇčgi, th…® wogiya weya Josuwa ghemba lagh…®ye regha, Tim…®nat Sera ina uu Epreim e lenji ghamba yakuyaku, e bobokuluko vanautumaniye. Va i vatada ghembako iyako na i yakuwe.   
\p
\v 51 Eliyesa iye ravowovowo, Josuwa Nan nariye, na randevivaŇčgi Isirel uu na uu e t…®nenji th…® giya thelauko iyako Ňčgoreiya var…®var…®ko var…®iwoko lenji govambwara \nd Giya Loi\nd* le renuwaŇča Sailo e t…®ne, e ghamba ruru Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye ghadidiye. Va e kamwath…®ke iyake th…® ten…®vao thelauko iyako.   
\c 20  
\s1 Ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye lolo i vo na ve kubarowe thoŇčgo i tagavamare thavwiya gheu regha  
\p
\v 1 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Josuwa iŇča,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúU dage weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® tuthiŇčgiya ghembaghemba ghamba kubaro Ňčgoreiye vama ya utugiya weya Mosese na i utu giya e ghen.  
\v 3 Iyako mbala the lolothan, i un…®gh…® thavwiya lolo regha, i vo na ve yakuwe na i vo iteta thela thoŇčgo i tamwetamwewe lith…® kaiwae.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 4 ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne ve vo vutha e ghambako iyako regha, wone ve ndeghath…® e ghamba ruruko na i utu giya le r…®gheko weŇčgiya ghembako giyagiyaniye budakai me yomarawe. Amba ne th…® vatomwe i ru e ghembako t…®ne na th…® wogiya le ghamba yaku na ve yakuwe.  
\v 5 ThoŇčgo thela nuwaiya i lith…®, na i mbele na ve vutha e ghembako iyako, giyagiyako ne th…® ndevaŇčgu giyaŇčge, mbala th…® vaŇčguthuwoleŇčge, kaiwae eŇčge mo un…®gh…® thavwiya ghanuko, ma me wein len gharegaith…®.  
\v 6 Loloko mbowo ne i yaku gheko ghaghad ne i ndeghath…® kot e marae na ghaghad kot…®ko gha ravakatha ‚ÄĒ iye ravowovowo lagh…®ye i mare. Amba loloko iyako i njogha e ghambae, ghembako iyava i vorikowe.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 7 Kaero th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya iyako. Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i njanja e yalasiko th…® tuthiŇčgiya ghembaghembake thiyake: Kades, Galili e t…®ne ‚ÄĒ bobokulu vanautumaniye na wabwi Nap…®talai lenji ghamba yakuyaku, Sekem ina e bobokulu vanautumaniye, uu Epreim e lenji ghamba yakuyaku na Hebron ina e bobokulu vanautumaniye, uu Juda e lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 8 Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro e boimako, Jeriko malamoniye e vuruvuru vwatavwatae val…®vaŇčga e boimako ghembaghembaniye thiyake: Beja ina wabwi Rubin lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne, Ramot Giliyad e t…®ne; wabwi Gad lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne; na Golan, ina Basan e t…®ne, wabwi Manase e lenji ghamba yakuyaku t…®ne.  
\v 9 Ghembaghembake lagh…®lagh…®ye thiyake ghamba thowa Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye na the lolothan…®va iye bwabwari, i yaku e t…®nenjiko kaiwanji. The lolothan thoŇčgo i un…®gh…® thavwiya lolo regha ne ve thowa weya iyako. I thowa weya the lolothan thoŇčgo i tamwetamwe na ne i lith…®we. Mane i lith…®we ghaghadi loloko iyako i ndeghath…® kot e marae.   
\c 21  
\s1 Ghembaghemba Livai gha uu lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 1 Amba wabwi Livai, uu na uu lenji randevivaŇčgi, th…® raka mena weŇčgiya Eliyesa iye ravowovowo, Josuwa Nan nariye na Isirel uu na uu e wabwi regha na regha t…®nenji lenji randevivaŇčgi,  
\v 2 Sailo, Kenani e t…®ne, th…®Ňča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* va i utura weya Mosese, iŇča, ‚ÄėHu giya ghembaghemba weime woya yakuwe na lama thetheghan…®ke lenji ghamba ghan evasiwanji.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Ňägoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i dagerako, Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® wogiya weŇčgi wabwi Livai ghembaghemba vavana na lenji ghamba yakuyaku tembe Ňčgoreiyeva lenji thetheghan…®ko lenji ghamba ghan e lenji thelauko t…®ne.   
\p
\v 4 Livai gha wabwi e t…®ne, Kohat gha uu va th…® wokaiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku. Uu na uu va th…® rimbun weya Eron, thiye va ravowovowoŇčgi na th…® wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku ghembayaworo na ghembato weŇčgiya wabwike thiyake ‚ÄĒ Juda, Simiyon na Benjamin.  
\v 5 Kohat gha uu e t…®ne vavanakova, th…® wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku ghembayaworo weŇčgiya wabwi Ip…®reim, Den na Manase, i ghembeghembeya yalasiko.   
\p
\v 6 Uu Gereson va th…® wogiya weŇčgi ghembaghemba ghembayaworo na ghembato e wabwike thiyake lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne: Isaka, Asa, Nap…®talai na Epreim val…®vaŇčga e boimako.   
\p
\v 7 Uu Merari va th…® wogiya weŇčgiya ghembaghemba ghembayaworo na ghembaiwo e wabwike thiyake lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne: Rubin, Gad na Sebulon.   
\p
\v 8 E var…®var…®ke var…®iwoke lenji woraŇčgiya e t…®ne, Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® wogiya ghembaghembake thiyake na thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan, wabwi Livai weŇčgi Ňčgora \nd Giya Loi\nd* va le utuutu weya Mosese.   
\p
\v 9 Wabwi Juda na Simion lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne va th…® giya ghembaghembake idaidanji thiyake:  
\v 10 weŇčgiya Eron orumburumbuye, thiye th…® rimbun Kohat gha uu t…®ne, iye i rimbun weya Livai. Thiye va th…® giyakaiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku Ňčgoreiya var…®var…®ma lenji woraŇčgiya.   
\p
\v 11 Va th…® giya weŇčgiya ghembaghemba thiyake: Kiriyat Aba (o Hebron) na thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan e ghadidiye. Va ina e bobokuluko vanautumaniye, wabwi Juda lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne (Aba iye Anak nariye).  
\v 12 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghembako lagh…®ye iyako na thetheghan…®ko lenji ghamba ghan weiye ghembaghemba nanasiye evasiwae kaerova Keleb Jepune nariye i wo le ghamba yakuyaku.   
\p
\v 13 Vama th…® wogiya Hebron (iye ghemba lagh…®ye ratagavamare lenji ghamba kubaro) na e vwata mbowo th…® giyava thiyake weŇčgiya Eron orumburumbuye: Lib…®na,  
\v 14 Jati, Estemowa,  
\v 15 Holon, Debi,  
\v 16 Ain, Juta na Bet Semes, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan. Ghembasiwoko thiyake inanji wabwi Juda na Simiyon e lenji ghamba yakuyaku t…®nenji.   
\p
\v 17 Wabwi Benjamin e lenji ghamba yakuyaku t…®ne th…® giya ghembaghembake thiyake weŇčgi: Gibiyon, Geba,  
\v 18 Anatot na Al…®mon weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.  
\v 19 Iya ghembayaworo na ghembatoke thiyake na thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan, th…® giya weŇčgiya ravowovowo th…® rimbun weya Eron.   
\p
\v 20 Kohat gha uu vavanava th…® giya ghembaghemba lagh…®lagh…®ye na lenji ghamba yakuyaku, wabwi Ip…®reim lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne. Iya ghembaghembake thiyake:   
\p
\v 21 inanji e bobokulu vanautumaniye, wabwi Ip…®reim lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne: th…® wogiya Sekem (ratagavamare lenji ghamba kubaro) na Geja,  
\v 22 Kib…®jaim na Bet Horon, ghembavar…® weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan…®.   
\p
\v 23 Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva wabwi Den lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne th…® wo El…®teke, Gibeton,  
\v 24 Aijalon na Gat Rimon, ghembavar…® weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.   
\p
\v 25 Manase gha wabwi lenji val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko, th…® wo Tanak na Gat Rimon, ghembaiwo weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.  
\v 26 Iya vara ghembayaworoke thiyake weinji thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan, uu Kohat th…® mban lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\p
\v 27 Mbowo uu reghava, Gereson i rimbun Livai e ghawabwi t…®ne th…® mbana lenji ghamba yakuyaku wabwi Manase, e boimako lenji ghamba yakuyaku t…®ne ghembaghembake thiyake: Golan ina Basan e t…®ne (ratagavamare lenji ghamba kubaro) na Be Estera, ghembaiwo weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.  
\v 28 Wabwi Isaka lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne th…® mbana ghembaghemba ghembavar…®ke thiyake: Kisiyon, Daberat,  
\v 29 Jamut na En Ganim, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan…®.  
\v 30 Wabwi Asa lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne th…® mbana ghembavar…®ke thiyake: Misal, Ab…®don,  
\v 31 Hel…®ka na Rehob, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.  
\v 32 Wabwi Nap…®talai lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne th…® mbana ghembatoke thiyake: Kades, Galili e t…®ne, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan…® (ratagavamare lenji ghamba kubaro), Hamot Do, na Katan, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan…®.  
\v 33 Uu regha na regha Gereson e t…®ne, th…® mban…®Ňčgiya ghembayaworo na ghembato, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.   
\p
\v 34 Wabwi Livai e t…®ne uu vavanakova ‚ÄĒ Merari gha uu th…® mbana ghembavar…® weŇčgiya wabwi Sebulon lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne. Ghembaghembake thiyake: Jok…®neyam, Kata,  
\v 35 Dim…®na na Nahalal, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.  
\v 36 Wabwi Rubin lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne th…® mbana ghembavar…®ke thiyake: Beja, Jahaj…®,  
\v 37 Kedemot na Mepat, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.  
\v 38 Wabwi Gad lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne th…® mbana ghembavar…®ke thiyake: Ramot ina Galili e t…®ne, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan (ratagavamare lenji ghamba kubaro), Mahanaim,  
\v 39 Hesbon na Jaje, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan.  
\v 40 Wabwi Merari th…® mbana lenji ghamba yakuyaku ghembayaworo na ghembaiwo.   
\p
\v 41 Ghembaghembako iya tari Livai lenji ghamba yakuyaku, inanji Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye e lenji ghamba yakuyaku t…®ne ghembaevar…® na ghembawa, weiye thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan e ghad…®d…®nji.  
\v 42 Ghemba regha na regha thetheghan lenji ghamba ghan vambe inanjiva e ghad…®d…®nji; iyake emunjoru e ghemba regha na regha t…®ne.   
\s1 Isirel th…® wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku e thelauko iyako t…®ne  
\p
\v 43 Kaero \nd Giya Loi\nd* i wogiya thelauko iyava i tholo na i dagerawe weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye orumburumbunji. MbaŇča kaero th…® wo ghamba yakuyakuko iyako amba thiya roghabanawe.  
\v 44 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha lenji yakuyaku i thovuye na th…® vanevane e val…®vaŇčgako lagh…®ye iyako e t…®ne, iya \nd Giya Loi\nd* vama i dagerako weŇčgiya orumburumbunji ne i wogiya weŇčgi. Ma tembe ghanjith…®gh…®yaŇčgiko regha i yondo vir…® na i gaith…®va weŇčgi, kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaerova i vakathaŇčgi na th…® kivwalavaoŇčgi.  
\v 45 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vamboromboro le dagerako wolagh…®ye iyava i dagerako weŇčgi.   
\c 22  
\s1 Wabwi theghewo na Manase gha uu vaŇčgothiye lenji ghamba yakuyaku  
\p
\v 1 Amba Josuwa i kula vathaŇčgiya wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase vaŇčgothiye,  
\v 2 na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero mendava hu vakathavao bigibigike wolagh…®ye, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo Mosese va i dage e ghemi na hu vakathaŇčgi, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva hu ghambugha bigibigike wolagh…®ye ghino va ya utuŇča na hu vakatha.  
\v 3 Kaero mbaŇča molao moli ghaghad vara mbaŇčake iyake, ma mbaŇča regha hu goriwoyathuŇčgiya lemi val…® bodaboda Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye. IyemaeŇčge, mendava hu vamboromboro budakaiya Giya lemi Loi va i wogiya e ghemi na hu vakatha.  
\v 4 MbaŇčake iyake Giya lemi Loi kaero i wogiya towo weŇčgiya lemi val…® bodabodake Ňčgoreiya va le dagerawe. Hu raka njogha e lemi ghamba yakuyaku, e thelauko iyava \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo, Mosese vama i wogiyako e ghemi Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako.  
\v 5 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbe hu njimbukiki wagiyawe budakaiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va utuŇča e ghemi, hu vakatha na hu ghambugha mbaroko \nd Giya Loi\nd* le rakakaiwo va i utugiya e ghemi. Va iŇča, ‚ÄėHu gharethova Giya lemi Loi e gharemina lagh…®ye na e unemina lagh…®ye.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 6 Amba Josuwa i giya ghanjidagemwaewo na i variyeŇčgi th…® raka njogha e lenji ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 7 WeŇčgiya wabwi Manase vaŇčgothiye regha Mosese vama i wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako, na weŇčgi vaŇčgothiye, Josuwa va i wogiya lenji ghamba yakuyaku Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji val…® bodaboda. MbaŇča kaero i giyavao ghanjidagemwaewo, i variyeŇčgi na  
\v 8 iŇča, ‚ÄúHu raka njogha e lemi ghamba yakuyaku weiye lemi bigibigi lemoyo moli, lemi thetheghan lemoyo moli, lemi silva, gol, brons na aiyan, na kwamakwamama lemoyo moli. Mbe vohu vegiya lemi bigibigina weŇčgiya lemi val…® bodaboda iya mendava hu mban weŇčgiya ghami rath…®gh…®yaŇčgina.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 9 Kaero ghar…®ghar…®ko thiye wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase vaŇčgothiye e boimako th…® vewareriŇča lenji ghamba yakuyaku. Th…® raka iteteŇčaŇčgiya lenji val…® Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye Sailo, Kenani e thelauniye, na th…® wareriŇča mbe thiye lenji thelau ina Giliyad e thelauniye t…®ne, iya vama th…® woko Ňčgoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* vama i dage weya Mosese.   
\s1 Ghamba vowo Jor…®dan e ghadidiye i womena vuyowo  
\p
\v 10 MbaŇča wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase vaŇčgothiye e boimako th…® raka vutha Gelilot, ina Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko, kaero th…® vatada ghamba vowo lagh…®ye regha na gha yamoyamo i thovuye gheko e walagh…®tako ghadidiye.  
\v 11 MbaŇča lenji val…® Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko th…® loŇčwe vaidiya iyako, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo hu vandeŇče! Ghar…®ghar…®ma wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase e boimako kaero th…® vatada ghamba vowo Gelilot e t…®ne, Jor…®dan ghadidiye ghinda ela val…®vaŇčgake.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Amba gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye e uuko wolagh…®ye val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko th…® raka vathavatha Sailo e t…®ne, na veth…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgiya wabwiko theghewo na Manase vaŇčgothiye iya weinjiyaŇčgi val…®vaŇčga e boimako.   
\p
\v 13-14 Amba ghar…®ghar…® inanji wabwi theyaworoma e t…®nenji th…® variyeŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana weŇčgiya wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase i vorovoro e thelau Giliyad t…®ne. Va th…® variya Pinehas, Eliyesa ravowovowo nariye, weiyaŇčgiya randeviva regha iya e uu regha na regha t…®ne. Iya uu regha na regha lenji randeviva theyaworoke thiyake, ghanji yavwatata i lagh…®ye e uu regha na regha t…®nenji.   
\p
\v 15 MbaŇča th…® raka mena Giliyad ele val…®vaŇčga, weŇčgiya wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase i vorovoro, amba th…® utu weŇčgi th…®Ňča,  
\v 16 ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* le ghar…®ghar…® e idanji wo utu weŇčga. Buda kaiwae hu goriwoyathu \nd Giya Loi\nd* na hu vatada ghamba vowo mbe ghemi kaiwami? Buda kaiwae na hu botewayathu Isirel lenji Loi na hu vakatha thar…® Ňčgoreiyako?  
\v 17 Wo hu renuwaŇča thar…®ma va ra vakatha Peyo e t…®ne, na ghambwera raithar…® regha i yomara na i gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo moli. Iyako kaiwae mbaŇčake mbe ra vavaidiya vuyowae. Ko amba ma val…®kaiwanda iya thar…®ko iyako?  
\v 18 Na e mbaŇčake iyake kaero hu botewava \nd Giya Loi\nd* gha ghambu? ThoŇčgo hu goriwoyathu \nd Giya Loi\nd* noroke, mbe evole vara ma i ghatemuru weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.  
\v 19 ThoŇčgo thelauna iya va hu wona ma val…®kaiwae hu kururuwe, hu raka mena \nd Giya Loi\nd* ele thelauko t…®ne iya le Mevathavathako Ňägoloniye inawe, na hu mbana thelau vavana e t…®nemeko. Ko iyemaeŇčge thava hu goriwoyathu \nd Giya Loi\nd* na hu goriwoyathuime na hu vatada ghamba vowo mbe ghemi kaiwami, naka ghamba vowoko iya Giya la Loi kaiwaeko, iya kaero inakowe.  
\v 20 Hu renuwaŇčakiki mbaŇča Eikan Jera nariye mava i ghambugha mbaro. \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i dage weinda na iŇča, ‚ÄėHu mukuwo bigibigina wolagh…®ye, e ghembana lagh…®ye Jeriko e t…®ne.‚Äô Iyako kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* i wogiya vuyowo taulagh…®ke weinda. Eikan le vakathako raithar…® kaiwae maa vambe ghamberegha eŇčge i vaidiya mare.‚ÄĚ   
\s1 Wabwi inanji Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro th…® vamanjamanjalaŇča ghamba vowoko kaiwae  
\p
\v 21 Amba wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase vaŇčgothiye e boimako th…® giya lenji thombe weŇčgiya randeviva wabwi regha na regha weŇčgi, na uu regha na regha val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko e t…®nenji, th…®Ňča,  
\v 22 ‚ÄúLoi mbe ReghaeŇčge Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye! Iye Giya! Loi mbe ReghaeŇčge Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye! Iye Giya! I ghareghare buda kaiwae menda wo vakatha iyake, na nuwameiya ghemi tembe hu ghareghareva! ThoŇčgo menda wo goriwoyathu na ma wo vatada lama loŇčweghath…® weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, mbema hu gabovaoime eŇčge!  
\v 23 ThoŇčgo ma menda wo ghambugha \nd Giya Loi\nd* na wo vatada ghamamberegha lama ghamba vowo na wo Ňčambu lama vowowe, o wo vakaiwoŇča lama mwaewo wit mbombouyewe o lama mwaewo v…®ghath…® vowoniye, hu viyathu na \nd Giya Loi\nd* tembe ghamberegha i giya vuyowo weime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 ‚ÄúNandere! Menda wo vakatha iyake kaiwae wo mararu ne iwaeŇčge mbaŇča i menamenako orumburumbumi tha muyaiko ne th…® dage weŇčgiya ghime orumburumbume na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėBudakai vara ne hu vakatha weya Giya, Isirel le Loi?  
\v 25 Amalagh…®niye va i vakatha Jor…®dan i tabo teghala weinda, ghime na ghemi uu Rubin na uu Gad. Ma tembe val…®kaiwamiva hu vakatha bigi regha weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.‚Äô Mbwatavole orumburumbumi th…® vakatha orumburumbume th…® viyathu \nd Giya Loi\nd* gha mararu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 26 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae woŇča, ‚ÄėWo ra vatada ghamba vowo, ko ma woŇča mwaewo ghamba Ňčambu o vowo kaiwae.‚Äô  
\v 27 Ko iyake, Ňčgoreiya nono ghime na ghemi e ghanda lughawoghawo na tha na tha muyaiko, mbema emunjoru wo kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* e Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye boboma weiye mwaewo gha ghambu kaiwae, na weiye vowo na v…®ghath…® ghanjimwaewa kaiwaeva. Ambane mbaŇča muyaiko orumburumbumi mane val…®kaiwanji th…® dage weŇčgiya ghime orumburumbume na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėMa tembe val…®kaiwamiva hu vakatha bigi regha weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 ‚ÄúVa lama renuwaŇča woŇča, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo nevole i yomara Ňčgoreiyako, orumburumbume val…®kaiwanji ne th…® thombe weŇčgi Ňčgoreiyake: Wo hu thuwe! Orumburumbume tha mevivako va th…® vatada ghamba vowo \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaiwae. Mava mwaewo ghanjighamba Ňčambu o vowo kaiwae, ko iyemaeŇčge Ňčgoreiya nono ghime na ghemi e ghanda lughawoghawo.‚Äô   
\p
\v 29 ‚ÄúEmunjoru ma tembe val…®kaiwameva wo goriwoyathu \nd Giya Loi\nd* o wo viyathu gha ghambu noroke na wo vatada ghamba Ňčambu vowo mwaewoŇčgi, wit na vowoŇčgi kaiwanji. Mane val…®kaiwae wo vatada tembe ghamba vowo reghava, nakama ghamba vowoko Giya La Loi kaiwae iya i ndeghath…® Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e ghamwaeko.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 30 MbaŇča Pinehas iye ravowovowo, na randeviva lagh…®lagh…®ye theyaworo va th…® raka menako weinji e uu regha na regha val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko, randeviva regha na regha e wabwi regha na regha e t…®nenji, th…® vandeŇče budakaiya wabwi Rubin, wabwi Gad na wabwi Manase vaŇčgothiye e boimako lenji utuutuko, kaero th…® wovatha.  
\v 31 Pinehas, iye Eliyesa ravorovoro nariye, i dage weŇčgiya wabwi Rubin, Gad na Manase vaŇčgothiye, iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake kaero wo ghareghare \nd Giya Loi\nd* iye weinda, kaiwae ma menda hu goriwoyathu e kamwath…®ke iyake. Kaero menda hu vamoruŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye \nd Giya Loi\nd* ele ghatemuru t…®ne.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 32 Amba Pinehas na randevivaŇčgima th…® raka iteteŇčgiya wabwi Rubin na wabwi Gad ghar…®ghar…®niye e thelau Giliyad t…®ne na th…® raka njogha Kenani ele val…®vaŇčga, weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® utu giya toto weŇčgi.  
\v 33 Weinji lenji warari th…® vandeŇče lenji utuutuko na th…® tarawe Loi. Na ma tembe th…® utuŇčava th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgiya wabwi Rubin na wabwi Gad ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® mukuwo lenji ghamba yakuyakuko.   
\p
\v 34 Wabwi Rubin na wabwi Gad ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® uno ghamba vowoko iyako idae ‚ÄúNono e ghanda lughawoghawoke,‚ÄĚ Giya iye Loi.   
\c 23  
\s1 Josuwa le utu moumouniye weŇčgi Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye  
\p
\v 1 MbaŇča molao moli kaero iko, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i giya vanevane weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye na th…® towo weŇčgiya ghanji rath…®gh…®yako wolagh…®ye evasiwanjiko. E mbaŇčako iyako Josuwa kaero i amalagh…®sar…® moli,  
\v 2 kaero i kula vathaŇčgiya Isirel uu na uu lenji randevivaŇčgiko wolagh…®ye: ghanjigiyagiyako, lenji randevivaŇčgiko, kot gha ravakathaŇčgi na ghar…®ghar…® lenji rakakaiwoŇčgi, na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ya amalagh…®sar…® moli wo theghathegha kaero i lagh…®ye e mbaŇčake iyake.  
\v 3 Kaerova hu thuwevao bigibigike wolagh…®ye Giya lemi Loi va i vakatha weŇčgiya vanautumake wolagh…®ye kaiwami. Giya lemi Loi va i gaith…® ghemi kaiwami.  
\v 4 Kaerova ya wogiya e ghemi uu na uu thelauko lagh…®ye Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako ghaghad Njigh…® Meditareiniyan, val…®vaŇčga e yalasiko, na lemi ghamba yakuyaku. Vama ya wogiya e ghemi thelauko lagh…®ye vanautuma na vanautuma lenji ghamba yakuyaku iya vama ra kivwalaŇčgiko, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva the vanautumaŇčgi amba mava ra kivwalaŇčgi.  
\v 5 Giya lemi Loi ne i vakathaŇčgi th…® voiteteŇčga, na ne i vambele yathuŇčgi na ghemi hu rakaru. Ne hu wo lenji ghamba yakuyaku Ňčgoreiya Giya lemi Loi va le dagera weŇčga.   
\p
\v 6 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae, mbe hu ghambu na hu vakatha wagiyawe bigibigina wolagh…®ye kaerova th…® rori njoŇča Mosese e le Mbaro gha buk t…®ne. Ne hu ndeghamaraviyathu val…®vaŇčga regha.  
\v 7 Ne hu ndev…®ghath…® weimiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iya mbe inanji e t…®nemina, na ne hu ndetholo lenji loiko e idaidanji, ne hu ndekururu o naŇčgo weŇčgi.  
\v 8 IyemaeŇčge, mbe hu vikikighath…® vara \nd Giya Loi\nd* Ňčgoreiya va hu vakavakatha ghaghad noroke.   
\p
\v 9 ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero i vagege yathuŇčgiya vanautuma lagh…®lagh…®ye na vur…®vur…®ghegheŇčgi e ghamwami, na hu rakarakaru, na ma tembe regha val…®kaiwaeva i gaith…® weŇčga.  
\v 10 The lolothan e t…®nemina, val…®kaiwae i vakatha hweserithaŇčar…® th…® raka vo, kaiwae Giya lemi Loi iye i gaith…® kaiwami, Ňčgoreiya va le dagerawe.  
\v 11 Mbe hu njimbukiki wagiyawe na hu gharethovuwe Giya lemi Loi.   
\p
\v 12 ‚ÄúKo iyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo hu ndeghereiyewana na hu tubwe weimiyaŇčgiya vanautumako thiyako ghar…®ghar…®niye iya mbe inanji e t…®nemina, na hu veghe weimiyaŇčgi,  
\v 13 amba ne hu ghareghare Giya lemi Loi mane tembe i vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgiva ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako, na ghemi hu wo lenji ghamba yakuyakuko. IyemaeŇčge, ne th…® tabo lemi ghamba dobuŇčgi, Ňčgoreiya ghaith…® o doda kaiwami na vir…®niye Ňčgoreiya gheyab…®yab…®b…® e wak…®nimi, na mb…®th…®mb…®th…® maramara e marami, ghaghad ma tembene ghemina regha i yakuyakuva e thelauke thovuye iya Giya lemi Loi vama i wogiyake e ghemi.   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúWo mbaŇča mare maiya vara. Taulagh…®na ghemi hu ghareghare e gharemi na e unemi Giya lemi Loi kaerova i giya e ghemi bigibigike thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye iyava i dageraweko. Dagerawe regha na regha va i vakatha i vamboromboro, ma tembe reghava i tagavakwara.  
\v 15 Ko iyemaeŇčge Ňčgoreiya va i vamboromboro dageraweko thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye e ghemi, tembene i vakathava Ňčgoreiye e the thar…® hu vakatha na i vamararuŇčga ghaghad ne i mukuwoŇčga e thelauke thovuye iyava i wogiyake e ghemi.  
\v 16 ThoŇčgo hu kivwala Giya lemi Loi le dagerawe iyava va utu giyana e ghemi, na ma vohu kaiwo weva loi vavana na hu kururu weŇčgi, Giya le ghatemuru ne i yomara e ghemi, na mane mbaŇča molao ma huya marevao e thelauke thovuye iya va i wogiyake e ghemi.‚ÄĚ   
\c 24  
\s1 Mbowo th…® vathiva dageraweko  
\p
\v 1 Josuwa i kula vathaŇčgi Isirel gha uuko wolagh…®ye na th…® raka mena th…® mevathavatha Sekem e t…®ne. MbaŇča th…® raka vuthavao, i ghatha raŇčgiyaŇčgi ghanji giyagiyako, lenji randevivaŇčgi, kot gha ravakathaŇčgi na Isirel lenji rakakaiwo lagh…®lagh…®ye na th…® raka mena na thiya ndeghath…® \nd Giya Loi\nd* ele YoŇčathowathowa Boboma ghamwae.   
\p
\v 2 Amba Josuwa i dage weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye, iŇča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd*, Isirel lenji Loi ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgora iyake, ‚ÄėMbaŇča mevivako olemi tatanakau va thiya yaku e Walagh…®ta Iupreitis val…®vaŇčga e boimako na th…® kururu weŇčgi loi kwan…®kwan. Lemi tatanakauko thiyako regha va idae Tira, Eibraham na Naho ramanji.  
\v 3a Ko iyemaeŇčge va ya vaŇčguraŇčgiya lemi tanakau Eibraham, Iupreitis val…®vaŇčga e boimako na ya vaŇčgughatharaŇča e thelauko lagh…®ye, Kenani t…®ne. Ya giyawe orumburumbuye lemoyo.‚Äô‚ÄĚ   
\b  
\p
\v 3b Ya wogiyawe nariye idae Aisake,  
\v 4 na weya Aisake ya giya le ŇčgaŇčga theghewo ‚ÄĒ Jeikob na Iso. Ya wogiyawe Iso vanautuma e ououniye idae Idom na le ghamba yakuyaku, ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob na le ŇčgamaŇčgama va th…® raka Ijipt.   
\p
\v 5 Va mbaŇča reghava ya variyeŇčgi Mosese na Eron, amba ya giya vuyowo lagh…®ye weŇčgi Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye, na ya vaŇčgu raŇčgiyaŇčga.  
\v 6 MbaŇča va ya vaŇčgu raŇčgiyaŇčgi orumburumbumi Ijipt e t…®ne, Ijipt lenji ragagaith…® th…® raka reghamba weŇčgi e waŇčga momod na hos…® ghanjirathatha lemoyo, ghaghad th…® raka mena Njigh…® Sosoro ghadidiye.  
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge orumburumbumi th…® kula voro weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* thalavu kaiwae na i variye momouwo e ghemi na thiye ghami lughawoghawo. I vakatha njigh…®ko na i bebe var…®var…®Ňčgi. Kaero hu ghareghare va ya vakatha budakai weŇčgi Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye. Amba hu yayaku e vuruvuru vwatavwata mbaŇča molao moli.   
\p
\v 8 Amba ya vaŇčgu menaŇčga Amori e lenji thelau, iyava thiya yaku Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga e boimako. Va th…® gaith…® weŇčga, ko iyemaeŇčge ya vakathaŇčga na hu vur…®gheghe kivwalaŇčgi. Ya mukuwoŇčgi e ghamwami na hu wo lenji thelauko lemi ghamba yakuyaku.  
\v 9 Amba Balak Jipo nariye, iye Mowab lenji kiŇč, i vivatha na i gaith…® weŇčga. I variye utuwe Balaam Beo nariye na i naŇčgowe i guraŇčga.  
\v 10 Ko iyemaeŇčge mava ya vatomwewe na i guraŇčga, vambema i giyagiya eŇčge ghami dage mwaewo na ya vaŇčgu raŇčgiyaŇčga Balak e n…®mae ghare.   
\p
\v 11 ‚Äú‚ÄėAmba hu raka lawa Jor…®dan na hu raka voro Jeriko. Gh…®mogh…®moru e ghembako iyako th…® gaith…® weŇčga, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva wabwi Amori, wabwi Perisi, wabwi Kenani, wabwi Hiti, wabwi Gegasi, wabwi Hivi na wabwi Jebusi, ko iyemaeŇčge ya vakathaŇčga na hu kivwalavaoŇčgi.  
\v 12 E ghamwami va ya vath…®na gharenji, na val…®kaiwae hu kivwalaŇčgi Amori lenji kiŇč theghewo. Mava hu vakatha iyako mbe ghemi e lemi gaith…® gha ghalith…® na mbwenara.   
\b  
\p
\v 13 ‚Äú‚ÄėVa ya wogiya e ghemi thelauko iya mava hu ndekabu mun ghan…®Ňčgawe na ghembaghemba mava hu vatad…®Ňčgi. MbaŇčake kaero huya yaku e t…®nenji na hu ghana vaen uneunenji na oliv…® uneunenji iya mava hu kabuŇčgi.‚Äô   
\p
\v 14 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae, mbaŇčake iyake mbe hu yavwatatawana \nd Giya Loi\nd* na hu kaiwowe weiye yawal…®mina lagh…®ye na lemi gharevatomwe emunjoru. Hu bigi yathuŇčgi loina iya orumburumbumi va th…® kurukururu weŇčgi Masepoteimiya na Ijipt e t…®nenji, na hu kaiwowe \nd Giya Loi\nd* mbe ghamberegha eŇčge.  
\v 15 ThoŇčgo \nd Giya Loi\nd* gha ghambu ma i lagh…®ye e gharemina, mbe noroke vara hu ghatha vakatha the loi ne hu kaiwowe, loiŇčgiko iya orumburumbumi va th…® kurukururu weŇčgi Masepoteimiya e t…®ne, o loiŇčgi iya Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® kururuke weŇčgi, iya lenji thelau huya yakuwe mbaŇčake. Ko iyemaeŇčge ghino na lo Ňčgoloke gharayakuyaku ne wo ghambu \nd Giya Loi\nd*.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 16 Ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® gonjoghawe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa val…®kaiwae tembe wo roiteteva \nd Giya Loi\nd* na wo ghambu loi vavana!  
\v 17 \nd Giya Loi\nd* lama Loi ghamberegha va i vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgi orumburumbume na ghime mbaŇča va wo tabona rakakaiwobwaga Ijipt e t…®ne, na wo thuweŇčgi vakatha amba rotaele lagh…®lagh…®ye va i vakathaŇčgi. Va i njimbukiki wagiyaweime na i gana ten…®tenime weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…® e vanautumako wolagh…®ye iyava wo raka ru e t…®nenjiko.  
\v 18 \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i vagege raŇčgiyaŇčgi vanautumako wolagh…®ye e ghamwame tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye iyava thiya yaku gheko. Iya kaiwae ghime tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ne wo ghambu \nd Giya Loi\nd*; kaiwae iye lama Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 19 Josuwa i dage weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko na iŇča, ‚ÄúMbwata mane val…®kaiwami hu ghambu \nd Giya Loi\nd*. Iye i boboma, na iye Loi yamwayamwakabuniye. Lemi goriwoyathu na lemi thar…®na wolagh…®ye mane i numoten.  
\v 20 ThoŇčgo hu roitete \nd Giya Loi\nd* na mavohu kaiwo weŇčgiva ghar…®ghar…® vavana lenji loi vatavatad…®, ne i gaith…® wanaŇčga na i giya vuyowo weŇčga. Ne i mukuwoŇčga moli othembe va i thovuye moli e ghemi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 21 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® dagewe Josuwa, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNandere! Ne wo ghambu \nd Giya Loi\nd*.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 22 Josuwa i dage weŇčgi, iŇča, ‚ÄúTembene ghamimbereghanava hu utuŇča emunjoru va hu tuthi ne hu ghambu \nd Giya Loi\nd*.‚ÄĚ  
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwana, mbe ghamamberegha vara wo utuŇčaime.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 23 Amba Josuwa, iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake hu bigiyathuvao ghar…®ghar…®na vavana lenji loiŇčgi iya inanjina weŇčga na hu vatomweŇčga emunjoru weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Isirel lenji Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 24 Ghar…®ghar…®ko th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNe wo kaiwowe \nd Giya Loi\nd* la Loi na wo ghambu.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 25 E mbaŇčako iyako Josuwa i ndeghath…® ghar…®ghar…®ko kaiwanji na i vakatha dagerawe thiye na \nd Giya Loi\nd* e ghanjilughawoghawo Sekem e t…®ne, na tembe ghekova i vakatha mbaro vavana na ghar…®ghar…®ko ne th…® ghambu.  
\v 26 Josuwa i rori njogha utuutuŇčgiko thiyako \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Mbaro gha Buk t…®ne. Amba i wo var…® lagh…®ye regha na i worawe e umbwa ouk raberabe, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye evasiwae.   
\p
\v 27 Kaero Josuwa i dage weŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko, iŇča, ‚ÄúVar…®ke iyake ne i tabo na ghanda rautuutu, kaiwae me loŇčwevao utuutuko wolagh…®ye \nd Giya Loi\nd* me utuŇčako weinda. Iyake ne i tabo ghami rautuutu na i vakathaŇčga thava hu goriwoyathu lemi Loi.‚ÄĚ   
\p
\v 28 Amba Josuwa i variye yathuŇčgi ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye, uu na uu e lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\s1 Josuwa i mare na th…® beku  
\p
\v 29 Bigibigiko wolagh…®ye thiyako e ghereinji, Josuwa Nan nariye i mare, gha theghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…® na hoyaworo.  
\v 30 Vambe th…® beku amalagh…®niye ele thelau Tim…®na Sera e t…®ne, e vanautuma ououniye uu Epreim lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne, Ou Gaas e ghaiwabuniyeko.   
\p
\v 31 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® ghambu \nd Giya Loi\nd* mbaŇča Josuwa na randevivaŇčgiko, iyava th…® thuwevao bigibigiko wolagh…®ye \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i vakathako weŇčgi Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye.   
\p
\v 32 Mevivako Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji tanakau regha Jeikob, va i vamodo thelau vuvura weŇčgiya Hamo le ŇčgamaŇčgama gh…®mogh…®moru, modae le lagh…®lagh…®ye silva gheth…®thaŇčar…®. MbaŇča Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® raka iteta Ijipt, thila mbana lenji tanakau regha, Josep wak…®wak…®ye. Vambe th…® mban…®mba loloŇčga vara e lenji loŇčgaloŇčgako wolagh…®ye t…®ne. E mbaŇčako vara iyako th…® beku e thelauko iya vuvurako iyako t…®ne, iya Jeikob va i vamodoko Sekem e t…®ne. Thelauko iyako Josep orumburumbuye lenji ghamba yakuyaku.   
\p
\v 33 Eliyesa, Eron rumbuye vambe i mareva na th…® beku e ghemba idae Gibeya. Ghembake iyake ina e vanautuma e ououniye uu Epreim lenji ghamba yakuyaku e t…®ne. Ghembako iyako vama th…® wogiyawe Eliyesa nariye, Pinehas.   